#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:90
msgid "Step 5: Understand the Editor Layout"
msgstr "ደረጃ 5፡ የአርታዒውን አቀማመጥ ይረዱ"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:92
msgid ""
"**Left panel** — The files for translation showing the progress of "
"translation and approval progress in percentage"
msgstr "** የግራ ፓነል *** - የትርጉም ፋይሎች የመተርጎሚያ እና የማጽደቅ ሂደት በመቶኛ"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:93
msgid ""
"**Centre panel** — The list of strings (phrases or sentences) waiting to be "
"translated. Untranslated strings are shown first. **(Red means untranslated,"
" Blue means translated but not approved, Green means translated and "
"approved)** ![Crowdin Translate "
"Colors](../_static/images/translation_guide/crowdin_translation_colorcode.png"
" \"Crowdin Translate Colors\")"
msgstr ""
"** የመሃል ፓነል *** - ለመተርጎም የሚጠባበቁ የሕብረቁምፊዎች ዝርዝር (ሀረጎች ወይም ዓረፍተ ነገሮች)። ያልተተረጎሙ"
" ሕብረቁምፊዎች መጀመሪያ ይታያሉ። **(ቀይ ማለት ያልተተረጎመ ማለት ነው፣ሰማያዊ ማለት ተተርጉሟል ግን አልፀደቀም ማለት"
" ነው፣አረንጓዴ ማለት ተተርጉሞ የፀደቀ ማለት ነው)** ![Crowdin Translate "
"Colors](../_static/images/translation_guide/crowdin_translation_colorcode.png"
" \"Crowdin Translate Colors\")"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:93
msgid "Crowdin Translate Colors"
msgstr "ክሮዲን ተርጓሚ ቀለሞች"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:96
msgid ""
"**Right panel** — The active string. You'll see the original English text at"
" the top, and a text field below where you type your translation. It also "
"contains suggestions from Translation Memory (TM), Machine Translation, and "
"the Glossary to help guide you."
msgstr ""
"** የቀኝ ፓነል *** - ንቁው ሕብረቁምፊ። ዋናውን የእንግሊዝኛ ጽሑፍ ከላይ እና ከታች የትርጉም ቦታዎን የሚተይቡበት "
"የጽሑፍ መስክ ታያለህ። እንዲሁም እርስዎን ለመምራት የሚረዱ የትርጉም ማህደረ ትውስታ (TM)፣ የማሽን ትርጉም እና "
"የቃላት መፍቻ ጥቆማዎችን ይዟል።"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:100
#, fuzzy
msgid "Step 6: Translate a String"
msgstr "ደረጃ 6፡ ሕብረቁምፊን ተርጉም።"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:102
msgid ""
"For the selected file, click on a string in the centre panel to select it."
msgstr "ለተመረጠው ፋይል፣ ለመምረጥ በመሃል ፓነል ላይ ያለ ሕብረቁምፊ ላይ ጠቅ ያድርጉ።"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:103
msgid "Read the English source text carefully in the centre panel."
msgstr "በመሃል ፓነል ውስጥ የእንግሊዝኛውን ምንጭ ጽሑፍ በጥንቃቄ ያንብቡ።"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:104
msgid "Type your translation in the text field below it."
msgstr "ትርጉምዎን ከስር ባለው የጽሑፍ መስክ ውስጥ ያስገቡ።"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:105
msgid ""
"Press **Enter** or click the green **Save** button to submit and move to the"
" next string."
msgstr ""
"ለማስገባት ** አስገባ *** ወይም አረንጓዴውን **አስቀምጥ** ቁልፍን ጠቅ ያድርጉ እና ወደ ቀጣዩ ሕብረቁምፊ ይሂዱ።"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:107
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"**Tip:** Watch for variables like `%1`, `{name}`, or `0` — do **not** "
"translate these. Copy them exactly as-is into the correct position in your "
"translation."
msgstr ""
"**ጠቃሚ ምክር:** እንደ `%1`፣ `{name}` ወይም `0` ያሉ ተለዋዋጮችን ይመልከቱ — እነዚህን ** አትርጉም**።"
" በትርጉምዎ ውስጥ ወደ ትክክለኛው ቦታ በትክክል ይቅዱዋቸው።"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:109
msgid ""
"You can also click a **TM suggestion** on the right panel to pre-fill your "
"translation field, then edit as needed."
msgstr ""
"እንዲሁም የትርጉም መስኩን ቀድመው ለመሙላት በቀኝ ፓኔል ላይ የ **TM ጥቆማን ጠቅ ያድርጉ እና እንደ አስፈላጊነቱ "
"ያርትዑ።"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:113
msgid "Step 7: Use Suggestions Wisely"
msgstr "ደረጃ 7፡ ጥቆማዎችን በጥበብ ተጠቀም"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:115
msgid ""
"Crowdin offers several aids to help you translate faster and more "
"consistently:"
msgstr "ክሮዲን በፍጥነት እና በወጥነት እንዲተረጉሙ የሚያግዙዎት ብዙ እርዳታዎችን ያቀርባል፡-"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:117
msgid ""
"**Translation Memory (TM)** — Shows how similar strings have been translated"
" before. A 100% match means the exact same string was translated previously."
" Use these as a starting point but always review them."
msgstr ""
"** የትርጉም ማህደረ ትውስታ (TM)** - ከዚህ በፊት ምን ያህል ተመሳሳይ ሕብረቁምፊዎች እንደተተረጎሙ ያሳያል። "
"100% ግጥሚያ ማለት አንድ አይነት ሕብረቁምፊ ከዚህ ቀደም ተተርጉሟል ማለት ነው። እነዚህን እንደ መነሻ ይጠቀሙ ነገር "
"ግን ሁልጊዜ ይገምግሟቸው።"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:118
msgid ""
"**Machine Translation (MT)** — Automatic suggestions from engines like "
"Google Translate or DeepL. These can be helpful but always need human review"
" and editing."
msgstr ""
"** የማሽን ትርጉም (ኤምቲ) *** - እንደ ጎግል ተርጓሚ ወይም DeepL ካሉ ሞተሮች የሚመጡ አውቶማቲክ ጥቆማዎች። "
"እነዚህ ጠቃሚ ሊሆኑ ይችላሉ ነገር ግን ሁልጊዜ የሰው ግምገማ እና አርትዖት ያስፈልጋቸዋል።"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:119
msgid ""
"**Glossary** — Highlighted key terms with approved translations. Always use "
"glossary terms for consistency across the project (e.g., specific climate or"
" weather terminology)."
msgstr ""
"** የቃላት መፍቻ** — የደመቁ ቁልፍ ቃላት ከጸደቁ ትርጉሞች ጋር። ሁልጊዜ የቃላት መፍቻ ቃላትን ለፕሮጀክቱ ወጥነት "
"ይጠቀሙ (ለምሳሌ፣ የተለየ የአየር ንብረት ወይም የአየር ሁኔታ ቃላት)።"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:123
msgid "Step 8: Working with Tasks"
msgstr "ደረጃ 8፡ ከተግባሮች ጋር መስራት"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:125
msgid ""
"Project managers may assign you specific **Tasks** — these are focused "
"batches of strings that need to be translated or proofread by a set "
"deadline. Tasks help the team coordinate effort and prioritise what gets "
"done first."
msgstr ""
"የፕሮጀክት አስተዳዳሪዎች ለየት ያሉ **ተግባራት** ሊሰጡዎት ይችላሉ - እነዚህ ያተኮሩ የሕብረቁምፊዎች ስብስቦች "
"በተወሰነ የጊዜ ገደብ መተርጎም ወይም ማረም አለባቸው። ተግባራት ቡድኑ ጥረቱን እንዲያቀናጅ እና መጀመሪያ ለሚደረገው "
"ነገር ቅድሚያ እንዲሰጥ ያግዛል።"

