"ትችላለህ - እያንዳንዱ አስተዋጽዖ ይቆጠራል!"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:146
msgid "Part 3 — Proofreading"
msgstr "ክፍል 3 - ማረም"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:148
msgid ""
"**Note:** Proofreader access is granted by project managers. If you'd like "
"this role, reach out to the ClimWeb community coordinators."
msgstr ""
"**ማስታወሻ፡** የማረጋገጫ አንባቢ በፕሮጀክት አስተዳዳሪዎች ተሰጥቷል። ይህን ሚና ከፈለጉ፣ የClimWeb ማህበረሰብ "
"አስተባባሪዎችን ያግኙ።"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:152
msgid "Step 9: What Proofreaders Do"
msgstr "ደረጃ 9፡ አራሚዎች የሚያደርጉት"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md:154
msgid ""
"Proofreaders review translations submitted by translators and give them the "
"final **approval** to be used on the ClimWeb platform. One can have both "
"translator and proofreader previlleges. As a proofreader, you:"
msgstr ""
"አረጋጋጭ አንባቢዎች በአስተርጓሚዎች የቀረቡ ትርጉሞችን ይገመግማሉ እና በClimWeb መድረክ ላይ ጥቅም ላይ የሚውሉትን "
