"በውይይት ላይ ይለጥፉ።"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md
msgid "4"
msgstr "4"

#: ../../_docs/Climweb-Translations-Contribution-Guide.md
msgid ""
"**Sound natural.** Translate the meaning, not word-for-word. Your "
