#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:9
msgid "Access Dashboard"
msgstr "ዳሽቦርድ ይድረሱ"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:11
msgid ""
"Logging into the ClimWeb automatically takes you to the Dashboard. If you "
"navigate away from the dashboard, you can return to it at any time by "
"clicking on the NMHS logo in the top-left section of your screen."
msgstr ""
"ወደ ClimWeb መግባት በራስ ሰር ወደ ዳሽቦርድ ይወስደዎታል። ከዳሽቦርዱ ርቀው ከሄዱ፣ በማያ ገጹ ላይኛው ግራ ክፍል "
"ላይ ያለውን የNMHS አርማ ጠቅ በማድረግ በማንኛውም ጊዜ ወደ እሱ መመለስ ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:14
msgid "The Dashboard"
msgstr "ዳሽቦርዱ"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:16
msgid ""
"The Dashboard is the main hub of the website. From the dashboard, you can "
"access all of the content you create in the ClimWeb as well as reports, "
"settings, and other content management features."
msgstr ""
"ዳሽቦርዱ የድረ-ገጹ ዋና ማዕከል ነው። ከዳሽቦርዱ ሆነው በClimWeb ውስጥ የሚፈጥሯቸውን ሁሉንም ይዘቶች እንዲሁም "
"ሪፖርቶችን፣ ቅንብሮችን እና ሌሎች የይዘት አስተዳደር ባህሪያትን ማግኘት ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/Find-Your-Way-Around.md:18
msgid "![Dashboard](../_static/images/navigating/Dashboard_1.png \"Dashboard\")"
