msgstr "አጠቃላይ የClimWeb አስተዳዳሪን ጨምሮ ለClimWeb ማስተባበር የመምሪያ የትኩረት ነጥቦችን ይለዩ"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:42
msgid "Installation and setup of ClimWeb in-premise servers/cloud servers"
msgstr "የClimWeb ውስጠ-ግቤት አገልጋዮች/ደመና አገልጋዮችን መጫን እና ማዋቀር"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:43
msgid ""
"Provision one-on-one training and capacity building to departmental focal "
"points on configuration and customization of the ClimWeb and Website"
msgstr ""
"በ ClimWeb እና ድረ-ገጽ ውቅረት እና ማበጀት ላይ ለመምሪያው የትኩረት ነጥቦች አንድ ለአንድ ስልጠና እና የአቅም "
"ግንባታ መስጠት።"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:44
msgid ""
"Provision of learning materials, documentations, and guides of the ClimWeb"
msgstr "የClimWeb የመማሪያ ቁሳቁሶች፣ ሰነዶች እና መመሪያዎች አቅርቦት"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:45
msgid "Follow-up support in troubleshooting and resolving technical bugs"
msgstr "ቴክኒካል ሳንካዎችን በመፍታት እና በመፍታት ላይ የክትትል ድጋፍ"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:47
msgid ""
"This also includes the implementation of CAP Alerts, Georeferenced data "
"visualization, email marketing, events, surveys, and user analytics "
"integration."
msgstr ""
"ይህ የCAP ማንቂያዎችን፣ የጂኦሬፈርሰንት ዳታ ምስላዊነትን፣ የኢሜል ግብይትን፣ ዝግጅቶችን፣ የዳሰሳ ጥናቶችን እና "
"የተጠቃሚ ትንታኔዎችን መቀላቀልንም ያካትታል።"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:49
msgid "**12. How does the ClimWeb work in low internet connectivity**"
msgstr "**12. ClimWeb በዝቅተኛ የበይነመረብ ግንኙነት እንዴት እንደሚሰራ**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:50
msgid ""
"The ClimWeb is optimized for low bandwidth scenarios. This involves the "
"minimisation of the use of large images, videos or heavy media files that "
"might consume a significant amount of bandwidth. The ClimWeb also supports "
"**caching mechanisms** that can help reduce the load on the server and "
"improve the website’s performance. By enabling caching, static content can "
"be stored on the user's device, reducing the need for repeated downloads, "
"and enhancing the experience on low bandwidth connections."
msgstr ""
"ClimWeb ለዝቅተኛ የመተላለፊያ ይዘት ሁኔታዎች የተመቻቸ ነው። ይህ ከፍተኛ መጠን ያለው የመተላለፊያ ይዘት ሊፈጁ "
"የሚችሉ ትልልቅ ምስሎችን፣ ቪዲዮዎችን ወይም ከባድ የሚዲያ ፋይሎችን አጠቃቀም መቀነስን ያካትታል። ClimWeb በአገልጋዩ"
" ላይ ያለውን ጫና ለመቀነስ እና የድር ጣቢያውን አፈጻጸም ለማሻሻል የሚረዱ ** የመሸጎጫ ዘዴዎችን ይደግፋል። መሸጎጫ "
"በማንቃት የማይለዋወጥ ይዘት በተጠቃሚው መሳሪያ ላይ ሊከማች ይችላል ይህም ተደጋጋሚ ማውረዶችን አስፈላጊነት በመቀነስ እና"
" ዝቅተኛ የመተላለፊያ ይዘት ባለው ግንኙነት ላይ ያለውን ልምድ ያሳድጋል።"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:53
msgid ""
"**13. Geo-referenced data visualization: What data sources and formats are "
"supported?**"
msgstr "**13. በጂኦ-የተጣቀሰ የመረጃ እይታ፡ ምን አይነት የመረጃ ምንጮች እና ቅርፀቶች ይደገፋሉ?**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:54
msgid ""
"An essential feature provided by the ClimWeb is its capability to "
"**facilitate interactive visualization of georeferenced data**. This "
"includes the ability to upload and visualize gridded data in formats such as"
" NetCDF and GeoTIFF, as well as vector data in the form of points and "
"polygons. The ClimWeb also supports the integration of CAP Alerts and "
"enables the inclusion of data from external Web Map Service (WMS) sources "
"for comprehensive data visualization."
msgstr ""
"በClimWeb የቀረበው አስፈላጊ ባህሪ ** በጂኦግራፊያዊ የተጠቀሰ ውሂብን በይነተገናኝ እይታን ማመቻቸት *** ነው። "
"ይህ እንደ ኔትሲዲኤፍ እና ጂኦቲኤፍኤፍ ባሉ ቅርጸቶች እንዲሁም የቬክተር መረጃን በነጥብ እና በፖሊጎን መልክ የመስቀል "
"እና የማሳየት ችሎታን ይጨምራል። ClimWeb የ CAP ማንቂያዎችን ውህደት ይደግፋል እና ከውጪ የድረ-ገጽ ካርታ "
"አገልግሎት (WMS) ምንጮች መረጃን ለአጠቃላይ የመረጃ እይታ ለማሳየት ያስችላል።"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:56
msgid "**14. Can they use the CAP editor alone?**"
msgstr "**14. የ CAP አርታዒን ብቻቸውን መጠቀም ይችላሉ?**"

#: ../../_docs/Frequently-Asked-Questions.md:57
msgid ""
"The CAP Editor has been developed to be flexible in its deployment options. "
"It can be run independently as a **standalone application**, which is "
"accessible at https://github.com/wmo-raf/cap-editor. Alternatively, it can "
"be fully **integrated into the ClimWeb**, providing seamless management of "
"CAP Alerts within the ClimWeb environment. More information about the "
"integration and usage can be found at https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-"
"cms/wiki/Manage-CAP-Alerts."
msgstr ""
"የCAP አርታዒው በማሰማራት አማራጮች ውስጥ ተለዋዋጭ እንዲሆን ተዘጋጅቷል። በ https://github.com/wmo-"
"raf/cap-editor ላይ የሚገኝ እንደ ** ራሱን የቻለ መተግበሪያ** ሆኖ ማሄድ ይችላል። በአማራጭ፣ በClimWeb "
"አካባቢ ውስጥ የCAP ማንቂያዎችን እንከን የለሽ አስተዳደር በመስጠት ሙሉ በሙሉ ** ወደ ClimWeb ሊዋሃድ ይችላል። "
"ስለ ውህደቱ እና አጠቃቀሙ ተጨማሪ መረጃ በ https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-cms/wiki/Manage-"
"CAP-Alerts ላይ ይገኛል።"

