msgstr ""
"[GeoManager](https://github.com/erick-otenyo/geomanager) - የጂኦ-ማጣቀሻ (ጂአይኤስ) "
"የውሂብ ስብስቦችን ለማስተዳደር እና ለማተም በይነተገናኝ በይነገጽ ያቀርባል"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:79
msgid ""
"[Administrative Boundary Manager:](https://github.com/erick-otenyo/adm-"
