#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:114
msgid "Developing new functionality"
msgstr "አዲስ ተግባር ማዳበር"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:116
msgid ""
"A modular approach is used when developing new functionality to be included "
"in the ClimWeb. The new functionality should be developed in isolation as a "
"Wagtail Python package and published on PyPi for installation using Pip."
msgstr ""
"በ ClimWeb ውስጥ የሚካተት አዲስ ተግባር ሲፈጠር ሞዱል አካሄድ ጥቅም ላይ ይውላል። አዲሱ ተግባር እንደ ዋግቴል "
"ፓይዘን ፓኬጅ ለብቻው መጎልበት እና ፒፕን በመጠቀም ለመጫን በPyPi ላይ መታተም አለበት።"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:119
msgid "We follow the following steps in general:"
msgstr "በአጠቃላይ የሚከተሉትን ደረጃዎች እንከተላለን."

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:121
msgid ""
"Explore existing packages in the Wagtail/Django community that provide "
"similar functionality."
msgstr "በWagtail/Django ማህበረሰብ ውስጥ ያሉ ተመሳሳይ ተግባራትን የሚሰጡ ጥቅሎችን ያስሱ።"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:123
msgid ""
"If an existing package exists and cannot be directly integrated into the "
"ClimWeb, we try to customize as much as we can on top of this package, to "
"make it interoperable. Otherwise, we use it directly"
msgstr ""
"አንድ ነባር ፓኬጅ ካለ እና በቀጥታ ወደ ClimWeb ሊጣመር የማይችል ከሆነ፣ በዚህ ፓኬጅ ላይ የቻልነውን ያህል "
"ለማበጀት እንሞክራለን። አለበለዚያ እኛ በቀጥታ እንጠቀማለን"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:126
msgid ""
"If we cannot find existing packages, then we develop the package from "
"scratch. The idea is to avoid reinvention of the wheel where possible."
msgstr ""
"ያሉትን ፓኬጆች ማግኘት ካልቻልን ጥቅሉን ከባዶ እናዳብራለን። ሀሳቡ በተቻለ መጠን የመንኮራኩሩን እንደገና መፈጠርን "
"ማስወገድ ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:129
msgid "Production Deployment"
msgstr "የምርት ማሰማራት"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:131
msgid ""
"[Docker](https://www.docker.com/) is used to containerize the different "
"components of the ClimWeb."
msgstr ""
"[Docker](https://www.docker.com/) የClimWebን የተለያዩ ክፍሎች ወደ መያዣ ለማስገባት ይጠቅማል።"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:133
msgid "Other containers used include"
msgstr "ጥቅም ላይ የዋሉ ሌሎች መያዣዎች ያካትታሉ"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:135
msgid ""
"[PostgreSQL](https://github.com/postgis/docker-postgis) with PostGIS "
"extension as the database"
msgstr ""
"[PostgreSQL](https://github.com/postgis/docker-postgis) በPostGIS ቅጥያ እንደ "
"ዳታቤዝ"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:137
msgid "[Nginx](https://hub.docker.com/_/nginx) as the webserver and web proxy"
msgstr "[Nginx] (https://hub.docker.com/_/nginx) እንደ የድር አገልጋይ እና የድር ፕሮክሲ"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:139
msgid ""
"[Memcached](https://hub.docker.com/_/memcached) as the caching system for "
"web requests"
msgstr "[መሸጎጥ](https://hub.docker.com/_/memcached) እንደ የድር ጥያቄዎች መሸጎጫ ሥርዓት"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:141
msgid ""
"[Eclipse Mosquitto](https://hub.docker.com/_/eclipse-mosquitto) as the MQTT "
"message broker. Mainly used for CAP alerts messaging"
msgstr ""
"[Eclipse Mosquitto](https://hub.docker.com/_/eclipse-mosquitto) እንደ MQTT "
"መልእክት ደላላ። በዋናነት ለ CAP ማንቂያዎች መላላኪያ ጥቅም ላይ ይውላል"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:144
msgid ""
"These are put into a docker compose configuration file, used to deploy the "
"project using Docker Compose."
msgstr ""
"እነዚህ Docker Compose ን በመጠቀም ፕሮጀክቱን ለማሰማራት ጥቅም ላይ የሚውለው ወደ ዶከር አዘጋጅ ማዋቀር ፋይል "
"ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:146
msgid ""
"An initialization repository is provided that brings together all the "
"different components into one project. This can be accessed at "
"[https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-cms-init](https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-"
"cms-init) . An installation guide is provided in the README file of the "
"repository."
msgstr ""
"ሁሉንም የተለያዩ አካላት ወደ አንድ ፕሮጀክት የሚያሰባስብ የማስጀመሪያ ማከማቻ ቀርቧል። ይህ "
"በ[https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-cms-init](https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-"
"cms-init) ላይ ማግኘት ይቻላል። የመጫኛ መመሪያ በማጠራቀሚያው README ፋይል ውስጥ ቀርቧል።"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:150
msgid "Managing Updates"
msgstr "ዝመናዎችን ማስተዳደር"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:152
msgid ""
"New releases with bug fixes and feature updates are periodically published "
"on the [nmhs-cms repository releases](https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-"
"cms/releases)."
msgstr ""
"አዲስ የተለቀቁ የሳንካ ጥገናዎች እና የባህሪ ማሻሻያ በየጊዜው በ[nmhs-cms ማከማቻ "
"ልቀቶች](https://github.com/wmo-raf/nmhs-cms/releases) ላይ ይታተማሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:155
msgid ""
"When there is a new release, The ClimWeb Admin interface will show a message"
" indicating that there is a new release. The Website administrator can then "
"choose to upgrade to the new version, after going through the release notes "
"that accompany every release."
msgstr ""
"አዲስ ልቀት ሲኖር የClimWeb Admin በይነገጽ አዲስ ልቀት እንዳለ የሚያመለክት መልዕክት ያሳያል። የድረ-ገጹ "
"አስተዳዳሪ ከእያንዳንዱ ልቀት ጋር ተያይዞ የሚለቀቁትን ማስታወሻዎች ካለፉ በኋላ ወደ አዲሱ ስሪት ለማሻሻል መምረጥ "
"ይችላል።"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:159
msgid ""
"The upgrade is through a click of a button, that triggers a docker build "
"process with the new versions. Once the new version is built successfully, "
"the container is restarted with the new version effected."
msgstr ""
"ማሻሻያው በአዲሶቹ ስሪቶች የመትከያ ግንባታ ሂደትን በሚያነቃቃ ቁልፍ ጠቅታ ነው። አዲሱ ስሪት በተሳካ ሁኔታ ከተገነባ "
"በኋላ መያዣው በአዲሱ ስሪት እንደገና ይጀምራል."

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:162
msgid ""
"![ClimWeb Update Button](../_static/images/technology/upgrade_button.png "
"\"ClimWeb Upgrade Button\")"
msgstr ""
"![ClimWeb Update አዝራር](../_static/images/technology/upgrade_button.png "
"\"ClimWeb Upgrade Button\")"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:162
msgid "ClimWeb Update Button"
msgstr "ClimWeb አዘምን አዝራር"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:164
msgid ""
"In rare cases where the automatic build trigger fails, the system admins are"
" trained to manually perform the upgrade"
msgstr ""
"አልፎ አልፎ አውቶማቲክ የግንባታ ማስጀመሪያው ካልተሳካ፣ የስርዓት አስተዳዳሪዎች ማሻሻያውን በእጅ እንዲሰሩ የሰለጠኑ "
"ናቸው።"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:166
msgid "Security in Django/Wagtail"
msgstr "ደህንነት በጃንጎ/ዋግቴል"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:168
msgid ""
"The ClimWeb, by using Django/Wagtail, out of the box contains the following "
"security features inbuilt. More details on each feature can be found at "
"[https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/5.0/topics/security](https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/5.0/topics/security/)"
msgstr ""
"ClimWeb፣ Django/Wagtailን በመጠቀም፣ ከሳጥኑ ውስጥ አብሮ የተሰሩ የሚከተሉትን የደህንነት ባህሪያት ይዟል። "
"በእያንዳንዱ ባህሪ ላይ ተጨማሪ ዝርዝሮች በ "
"[https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/5.0/topics/security] "
"(https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/5.0/topics/security/) ላይ ይገኛሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:172
msgid "Cross site scripting (XSS) protection"
msgstr "የጣቢያ ስክሪፕት (XSS) ጥበቃ"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:173
msgid "Cross site request forgery (CSRF) protection"
msgstr "የመስቀለኛ ቦታ ጥያቄ የውሸት (CSRF) ጥበቃ"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:174
msgid "SQL Injection protection"
msgstr "SQL መርፌ ጥበቃ"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:175
msgid "Clickjacking protection"
msgstr "የጠቅታ ጥበቃ"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:176
msgid "SSL\\HTTPS protection settings"
msgstr "SSL\\HTTPS ጥበቃ ቅንብሮች"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:177
msgid "Host header validation"
msgstr "የአስተናጋጅ ራስጌ ማረጋገጫ"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:178
msgid "Referrer Policy Protection"
msgstr "የማጣቀሻ ፖሊሲ ጥበቃ"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:179
msgid "Cross-origin opener policy"
msgstr "ተሻጋሪ መክፈቻ ፖሊሲ"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:180
msgid "Session Security"
msgstr "የክፍለ ጊዜ ደህንነት"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:181
msgid "User-uploaded content protection"
msgstr "በተጠቃሚ የተጫነ የይዘት ጥበቃ"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:183
msgid "ClimWeb Specific security features:"
msgstr "ClimWeb የተወሰኑ የደህንነት ባህሪያት፡-"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:185
msgid "Ability to change admin url periodically"
msgstr "የአስተዳዳሪ ዩአርኤልን በየጊዜው የመቀየር ችሎታ"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:186
msgid "Daily backup mechanisms"
msgstr "ዕለታዊ የመጠባበቂያ ዘዴዎች"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:187
msgid "Brute force login preventions"
msgstr "በጉልበት የመግባት መከላከያ"

#: ../../_docs/Technology.md:188
msgid "2 Factor Authentication for administrator account"
msgstr "ለአስተዳዳሪ መለያ 2 የምክንያት ማረጋገጫ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:1
msgid "Creating a Dashboard Page"
msgstr "የዳሽቦርድ ገጽ መፍጠር"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:3
msgid "When creating a new Dashboard Page:"
msgstr "አዲስ ዳሽቦርድ ገጽ ሲፈጥሩ፡-"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:5
msgid ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/dashboard_banner.png \"ClimWeb "
"Atlas\")"
msgstr ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/dashboard_banner.png \"ClimWeb "
"Atlas\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard-Gallery.md:10
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard-Gallery.md:15
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard-Gallery.md:17
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard-Gallery.md:19
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard-Gallery.md:23
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard-Gallery.md:27
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:5
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:17
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:7
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:20
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:22
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:30
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:42
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Snippets.md:45
#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/index.md:3
msgid "ClimWeb Atlas"
msgstr "ClimWeb አትላስ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:7
msgid ""
"Enter a **page title**, **banner title** and optional **banner "
"description**."
msgstr "**የገጽ ርዕስ**፣ **የባነር ርዕስ** እና አማራጭ **የባነር መግለጫ** ያስገቡ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:8
msgid ""
"Choose a **background color** (theme for the atlas that will be used for "
"section headings) and **banner image** if desired."
msgstr "ከፈለጉ **የጀርባ ቀለም** (የአትላስ ጭብጥ ለክፍል አርእስቶች የሚውል) እና **የባነር ምስል** ይምረጡ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:9
msgid ""
"In the body, add sections containing content using reusable **blocks** "
"(explained below). Each Section requires a section title and description. "
"You can build dashboards using different block types:"
msgstr ""
"በሰውነት ውስጥ, እንደገና ጥቅም ላይ ሊውል የሚችል ** እገዳዎች ** (ከዚህ በታች ተብራርቷል) በመጠቀም ይዘት የያዙ "
"ክፍሎችን ያክሉ። እያንዳንዱ ክፍል የክፍል ርዕስ እና መግለጫ ይፈልጋል። የተለያዩ የማገጃ ዓይነቶችን በመጠቀም "
"ዳሽቦርዶችን መገንባት ይችላሉ፡-"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:11
msgid ""
"**Title & Text Block** – Simple block for adding a section heading and "
"supporting text."
msgstr "** ርዕስ እና የጽሑፍ አግድ *** - የክፍል ርዕስ ለመጨመር እና ጽሑፍን ለመደገፍ ቀላል እገዳ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:12
msgid ""
"**Title, Text & Image Block** – A heading, text, and image side by side."
msgstr "** ርዕስ ፣ ጽሑፍ እና ምስል አግድ *** - ርዕስ ፣ ጽሑፍ እና ምስል ጎን ለጎን።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:13
msgid "**Table Block** – Add tabular data (rows and columns)."
msgstr "** የሠንጠረዥ እገዳ *** - የሰንጠረዥ ውሂብ አክል (ረድፎች እና አምዶች)።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:14
msgid "**Map Block** – Display an interactive map (from a Map Snippet)."
msgstr "** የካርታ እገዳ *** - በይነተገናኝ ካርታ አሳይ (ከካርታ ቅንጣቢ)።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:15
msgid "**Chart Block** – Display a chart (from a Chart Snippet)."
msgstr "** የገበታ እገዳ *** - ገበታ አሳይ (ከገበታ ቅንጣቢ)።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:17
msgid ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/dashboard_blocks.png \"ClimWeb "
"Atlas\")"
msgstr ""
"![ClimWeb Atlas](../../_static/images/atlas/dashboard_blocks.png \"ClimWeb "
"Atlas\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard.md:19
msgid ""
"Once blocks are added, scroll to the bottom of the page. Click **Save "
"Draft** to preview or **Publish** to make the dashboard live."
msgstr ""
"አንዴ እገዳዎች ከተጨመሩ በኋላ ወደ የገጹ ግርጌ ይሸብልሉ. ለማየት ** ረቂቅን አስቀምጥ ** ን ጠቅ ያድርጉ ወይም "
"ዳሽቦርዱን ቀጥታ ለማድረግ ** አትም*።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard-Gallery.md:1
msgid "Creating Dashboard Gallery"
msgstr "ዳሽቦርድ ጋለሪ መፍጠር"

#: ../../_docs/manage_atlas/Create-Dashboard-Gallery.md:3
msgid "This section will guide you create and manage dashboards in an Atlas."
