msgstr ""
"**የአደጋ ዓይነት**፡ የአደጋው ዓይነት ስም። ከ WMO አስቀድሞ ከተገለጸው ዝርዝር ውስጥ መምረጥ ወይም አዲስ መፍጠር "
"ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Base-Settings.md:33
msgid ""
"**Category**: The category of the hazard type, as defined in the CAP "
"Protocol."
msgstr "** ምድብ ***: በ CAP ፕሮቶኮል ላይ እንደተገለጸው የአደጋው ዓይነት ምድብ."

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Base-Settings.md:34
msgid ""
"**Event Code**: The event code of the hazard type, as defined in [OASIS "
"Event Term List for use with CAP](https://docs.oasis-open.org/emergency/cap-"
"etl/v1.2/cn01/cap-etl-v1.2-cn01.html). When selecting the event code, ensure"
" you have the correct hazard Category selected, as the event codes are "
"filtered by the selected hazard Category. You can confirm the event code by "
"checking the [OASIS Event Terms](https://docs.oasis-open.org/emergency/cap-"
"etl/v1.2/cn01/cap-etl-v1.2-cn01.html). Scroll down to the Appendix B "
"section, where the event codes are listed with the corresponding Category."
msgstr ""
"**የክስተት ኮድ**፡ የአደጋው አይነት የክስተት ኮድ፣ በ[OASIS የክስተት ቃል ዝርዝር ከ CAP ጋር ለመጠቀም] "
"(https://docs.oasis-open.org/emergency/cap-etl/v1.2/cn01/cap-"
"etl-v1.2-cn01.html) ላይ እንደተገለጸው። የክስተቱን ኮድ በሚመርጡበት ጊዜ የክስተት ኮዶች በተመረጠው የአደጋ "
"ምድብ ስለሚጣሩ ትክክለኛውን የአደጋ ምድብ መምረጥዎን ያረጋግጡ። [OASIS የክስተት "
"ውል](https://docs.oasis-open.org/emergency/cap-etl/v1.2/cn01/cap-"
"etl-v1.2-cn01.html) በመፈተሽ የክስተት ኮዱን ማረጋገጥ ትችላለህ። ወደ አባሪ ለ ክፍል ወደታች ይሸብልሉ፣ "
"የክስተት ኮዶች ከተዛማጅ ምድብ ጋር ተዘርዝረዋል።"

