#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:5
msgid ""
"The CAPComposer tool is a solution that provides a range of functionalities "
"to support the NMHS in seamlessly issuing CAP. It has been developed with an"
" aim of increasing the adoption of CAP by NMHS in Africa."
msgstr ""
"የCAPComposer መሳሪያ ኤንኤምኤችኤስ ያለችግር CAP ለማውጣት የተለያዩ ተግባራትን የሚሰጥ መፍትሄ ነው። በአፍሪካ "
"ኤን ኤም ኤች ኤስ የ CAP ጉዲፈቻን ለማሳደግ በማለም ነው የተዘጋጀው።"

