#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:13
msgid "🌟 Features"
msgstr "🌟 ባህሪዎች"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:15
msgid ""
"Modern user-friendly composer that follows [CAP 1.2](http://docs.oasis-"
"open.org/emergency/cap/v1.2/CAP-v1.2-os.html) standard. Built on top of the "
"awesome [Wagtail CMS](https://wagtail.org)"
msgstr ""
"[CAP 1.2](http://docs.oasis-open.org/emergency/cap/v1.2/CAP-v1.2-os.html) "
"ደረጃን የሚከተል ዘመናዊ ለተጠቃሚ ምቹ አቀናባሪ። በአስደናቂው [Wagtail CMS](https://wagtail.org) "
"ላይ የተሰራ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:17
msgid ""
"Preview a CAP alert as you edit. Save drafts for sharing with colleagues and"
" collaborating"
msgstr ""
"በሚያርትዑበት ጊዜ የ CAP ማንቂያ አስቀድመው ይመልከቱ። ከስራ ባልደረቦች ጋር ለመጋራት እና ለመተባበር ረቂቆችን "
"ያስቀምጡ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:18
msgid ""
"Inbuilt CAP validation. The page will not save if you have not input the "
"required data according to CAP standard"
msgstr "አብሮ የተሰራ CAP ማረጋገጫ። በ CAP መስፈርት መሰረት አስፈላጊውን ውሂብ ካላስገባ ገጹ አይቀመጥም"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:19
msgid ""
"User-friendly alert area map tool that allows multiple ways of constructing "
"alert geographic areas, while keeping the interface simple"
msgstr ""
"በይነገጹን ቀላል በማድረግ በርካታ የማስጠንቀቂያ ጂኦግራፊያዊ አካባቢዎችን ለመገንባት የሚያስችል ለተጠቃሚ ምቹ የማንቂያ "
"ቦታ ካርታ መሳሪያ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:21
msgid "Upload and use your country/territory's administrative boundaries"
msgstr "የአገርዎን/የግዛትዎን የአስተዳደር ወሰኖች ይስቀሉ እና ይጠቀሙ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:22
msgid "Draw a polygon"
msgstr "ፖሊጎን ይሳሉ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:23
msgid "Draw a circle"
msgstr "ክብ ይሳሉ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:24
msgid ""
"Selecting predefined areas that you create beforehand for common alert areas"
msgstr "ለጋራ ማንቂያ ቦታዎች አስቀድመው የሚፈጥሯቸውን አስቀድመው የተገለጹ ቦታዎችን መምረጥ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:25
msgid ""
"Inbuilt publishing workflow using Wagtail's powerful page model, with "
"automated emails to composers and approvers"
msgstr ""
"አብሮ የተሰራ የሕትመት የስራ ፍሰት የWagtailን ኃይለኛ የገጽ ሞዴል በመጠቀም፣ አውቶማቲክ ኢሜይሎች ለአቀናባሪዎች "
"እና አዘጋጆች"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:26
msgid ""
"Collaborate with team members using inbuilt comments (similar to how you "
"could do in Word) with automated notifications. Request for changes and "
"approvals"
msgstr ""
"አብሮ የተሰሩ አስተያየቶችን በመጠቀም ከቡድን አባላት ጋር ይተባበሩ (በዎርድ ውስጥ እንዴት ማድረግ እንደሚችሉ አይነት) "
"ከራስ-ሰር ማሳወቂያዎች ጋር። ለውጦችን እና ማጽደቆችን ይጠይቁ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:28
msgid ""
"Publish realtime notifications/messages to third party integrations using "
"MQTT messaging protocol"
msgstr ""
"MQTT የመልእክት መላላኪያ ፕሮቶኮልን በመጠቀም አሁናዊ ማሳወቂያዎችን/መልእክቶችን ለሶስተኛ ወገን ውህደቶች ያትሙ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:29
msgid ""
"Predefine a list of hazards types monitored by your institution, with "
"intuitive icons from [OCHA humanitarian "
"icons](https://brand.unocha.org/d/xEPytAUjC3sH/icons#/humanitarian-icons)"
msgstr ""
"ከ[OCHA የሰብአዊነት "
"አዶዎች](https://brand.unocha.org/d/xEPytAUjC3sH/icons#/humanitarian-icons) "
"በሚታዩ አዶዎች በተቋምዎ ክትትል የሚደረግባቸውን የአደጋ ዓይነቶች ዝርዝር አስቀድመው ይግለጹ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/CAP-Features.md:31
msgid ""
"Extendable to add your custom logic and functionality. The package provides "
"an `abstract` django model that can be inherited for customizations."
msgstr ""
"የእርስዎን ብጁ አመክንዮ እና ተግባራዊነት ለመጨመር የተዘረጋ። ጥቅሉ ለማበጀት ሊወረስ የሚችል የ‹abstract› "
"django ሞዴል ያቀርባል።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/Composer-and-Approver.md:1
msgid "CAP Composer and Approver Roles and Publishing Workflows"
msgstr "CAP አቀናባሪ እና ሚናዎችን አጽዳቂ እና የስራ ፍሰቶችን ማተም"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/Composer-and-Approver.md:3
msgid ""
"Within CAP, roles such as \"Composer\" and \"Approver\" are essential to "
"ensure the accuracy and authorization of alerts before dissemination."
msgstr ""
"በ CAP ውስጥ፣ ከማሰራጨቱ በፊት የማንቂያዎችን ትክክለኛነት እና ፍቃድ ለማረጋገጥ እንደ \"አቀናባሪ\" እና "
"\"አጽዳቂ\" ያሉ ሚናዎች አስፈላጊ ናቸው።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/Composer-and-Approver.md:5
msgid "**CAP Composer Role:**"
msgstr "**CAP የሙዚቃ አቀናባሪ ሚና፡**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/Composer-and-Approver.md:7
msgid ""
"A CAP Composer is responsible for creating and drafting alert messages. This"
" role involves collecting pertinent information about an incident and "
"structuring it according to the CAP format. The Composer ensures that all "
"necessary details are included to inform the public or specific agencies "
"effectively."
msgstr ""
"የ CAP አቀናባሪ የማንቂያ መልዕክቶችን የመፍጠር እና የማዘጋጀት ሃላፊነት አለበት። ይህ ሚና ስለ አንድ ክስተት "
"አግባብነት ያለው መረጃ መሰብሰብ እና በ CAP ቅርጸት መሰረት ማዋቀርን ያካትታል። አቀናባሪው ለህዝብ ወይም ለተወሰኑ "
"ኤጀንሲዎች ውጤታማ በሆነ መንገድ ለማሳወቅ ሁሉም አስፈላጊ ዝርዝሮች መጨመሩን ያረጋግጣል።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/Composer-and-Approver.md:9
msgid "**CAP Approver Role:**"
msgstr "** CAP አጽዳቂ ሚና፡**"

#: ../../_docs/manage_cap/Composer-and-Approver.md:11
msgid ""
"The CAP Approver reviews the alerts composed by the Composer. This role is "
"crucial for validating the content, ensuring compliance with organizational "
"protocols, and authorizing the release of the alert to the intended "
"audience. The Approver acts as a quality control measure to prevent the "
"dissemination of incorrect or unauthorized information."
msgstr ""
"የCAP አጽዳቂው በአቀናባሪው የተቀናበሩ ማንቂያዎችን ይገመግማል። ይህ ሚና ይዘቱን ለማረጋገጥ፣ ከድርጅታዊ ፕሮቶኮሎች "
