msgstr "አካባቢ / ከተማ ትንበያ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:6
msgid "Currently active Weather Warnings,"
msgstr "በአሁኑ ጊዜ ንቁ የአየር ሁኔታ ማስጠንቀቂያዎች ፣"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:7
msgid "Up to 5 Geomanager/MapViewer Layers (if enabled)"
msgstr "እስከ 5 ጂኦማናጀር/MapViewer ንብርብሮች (ከነቃ)"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:9
msgid ""
"![Homepage Map](../../_static/images/settings/homepagemap/homepage-map.png "
"\"Homepage Map\")"
msgstr ""
"![የመነሻ ገጽ ካርታ](../../_static/images/settings/homepagemap/Homepage-map.png "
"\"የመነሻ ገጽ ካርታ\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:9
msgid "Homepage Map"
msgstr "የመነሻ ገጽ ካርታ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:13
msgid ""
"You can modify the homepage map settings from the settings menu on the left "
"side-bar of the Admin interface. *Scroll down if settings menu is not "
"visible*."
msgstr ""
"በአስተዳዳሪ በይነገጽ በግራ በኩል ባለው አሞሌ ላይ ካለው የቅንጅቶች ምናሌ የመነሻ ገጽ ካርታ ቅንብሮችን ማስተካከል "
"ይችላሉ። * የቅንብሮች ሜኑ የማይታይ ከሆነ ወደ ታች ይሸብልሉ*።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:16
msgid "Click on (1)Settings > (2) Homepage map settings"
msgstr "(1) ቅንጅቶች > (2) የመነሻ ገጽ ካርታ መቼቶች ላይ ጠቅ ያድርጉ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:18
msgid ""
"![Homepage Map Settings](../../_static/images/settings/homepagemap/homepage-"
"map-settings.png \"Homepage Map Settings\")"
msgstr ""
"![የመነሻ ገጽ ካርታ ቅንጅቶች](../../_static/images/settings/homepagemap/ሆምፔጅ-ካርታ-"
"settings.png \"የመነሻ ገጽ ካርታ ቅንጅቶች\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:22
msgid ""
"![Boundary and CAP "
"Settings](../../_static/images/settings/homepagemap/boundary_and_cap_settings.png"
" \"Boundary CAP Settings\")"
msgstr ""
"![የድንበር እና የካፒታል "
"ቅንጅቶች](.../../_static/images/settings/homepagemap/boundary_and_cap_settings.png"
" \"Boundary CAP Settings)\""

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:22
msgid "Boundary and CAP Settings"
msgstr "የድንበር እና የኬፕ ቅንጅቶች"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:24
msgid ""
"**Show Level 1 Boundaries**: Check this box to show the level 1 boundaries "
"on the map. By default, this is disabled to reduce the bandwidth required to"
" load the map."
msgstr ""
"**ደረጃ 1 ድንበሮችን አሳይ**፡ የደረጃ 1 ድንበሮችን በካርታው ላይ ለማሳየት በዚህ ሳጥን ላይ ምልክት ያድርጉ። "
"በነባሪ፣ ካርታውን ለመጫን የሚያስፈልገውን የመተላለፊያ ይዘት ለመቀነስ ይህ ተሰናክሏል።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:26
msgid ""
"**Use Geomanager Basemaps**: Check this box to use the Geomanager basemaps "
"instead of the default basemaps. This is useful if you have configured "
"custom basemaps in Geomanager."
msgstr ""
"**የጂኦማኔጀር ቤዝማፕስን ተጠቀም**፡ ከነባሪው ቤዝ ካርታዎች ይልቅ የጂኦማኔጀር ቤዝ ካርታዎችን ለመጠቀም በዚህ ሳጥን "
"ላይ ምልክት አድርግ። በጂኦማኔጀር ውስጥ ብጁ የመሠረት ካርታዎችን ካዋቀሩ ይህ ጠቃሚ ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:29
msgid "CAP Warnings Settings"
msgstr "የ CAP ማስጠንቀቂያዎች ቅንጅቶች"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:31
msgid ""
"**Show CAP Warnings Layer**: Check this box to show the currently active CAP"
" warnings on the map. Checked by default. This layer is only shown on the "
"map when there is at least one active CAP warning."
msgstr ""
"**የካፕ ማስጠንቀቂያዎች ንብርብርን አሳይ**፡ በአሁኑ ጊዜ ንቁ የሆኑትን የ CAP ማስጠንቀቂያዎች በካርታው ላይ "
"ለማሳየት በዚህ ሳጥን ላይ ምልክት ያድርጉ። በነባሪነት ተረጋግጧል። ይህ ንብርብር በካርታው ላይ የሚታየው ቢያንስ አንድ "
"ገቢር CAP ማስጠንቀቂያ ሲኖር ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:33
msgid ""
"**CAP Warnings Layer Display Name**: This is the name of the CAP warnings "
"layer that will be displayed on the map. By default, it is set to `Weather "
"Warnings`. You can change it, for example, to the corresponding language of "
"your Climweb Instance."
msgstr ""
"**የ CAP ማስጠንቀቂያዎች ንብርብር ማሳያ ስም**፡ ይህ በካርታው ላይ የሚታየው የ CAP ማስጠንቀቂያ ንብርብር ስም "
"ነው። በነባሪነት ወደ «የአየር ሁኔታ ማስጠንቀቂያዎች» ተቀናብሯል። ሊለውጡት ይችላሉ፣ ለምሳሌ፣ ወደ የእርስዎ "
"Climweb ምሳሌ ተጓዳኝ ቋንቋ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:38
msgid "Location Forecast Layer"
msgstr "የአካባቢ ትንበያ ንብርብር"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:40
msgid ""
"![Location Forecast Layer "
"Settings](../../_static/images/settings/homepagemap/location_forecast_settings.png"
" \"Location Forecast Settings\")"
msgstr ""
"![የአካባቢ ትንበያ የንብርብር "
"ቅንጅቶች](../../_static/images/settings/Homepagemap/location_forecast_settings.png"
" \"የአካባቢ ትንበያ ቅንጅቶች\""

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:40
msgid "Location Forecast Layer Settings"
msgstr "የአካባቢ ትንበያ የንብርብር ቅንብሮች"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:42
msgid ""
"**Show Location Forecast Layer**: Check this box to show the location "
"forecast layer on the map. This layer shows the forecast for different "
"cities as set in the system. By default, this is enabled."
msgstr ""
"** የአካባቢ ትንበያ ንብርብርን አሳይ ***፡ በካርታው ላይ ያለውን የአካባቢ ትንበያ ንብርብር ለማሳየት በዚህ ሳጥን "
"ላይ ምልክት ያድርጉ። ይህ ንብርብር በስርዓቱ ውስጥ በተቀመጠው መሰረት ለተለያዩ ከተሞች ያለውን ትንበያ ያሳያል. በነባሪ"
" ይህ ነቅቷል።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:44
msgid ""
"**Location Forecast Layer Display Name**: This is the name of the location "
"forecast layer that will be displayed on the map. By default, it is set to "
"`Location Forecast`. You can change it, for example, to the corresponding "
"language of your Climweb Instance."
msgstr ""
"**የቦታ ትንበያ የንብርብር ማሳያ ስም**፡ ይህ በካርታው ላይ የሚታየው የአካባቢ ትንበያ ንብርብር ስም ነው። በነባሪነት"
" ወደ `አካባቢ ትንበያ' ተቀናብሯል። ሊለውጡት ይችላሉ፣ ለምሳሌ፣ ወደ የእርስዎ Climweb ምሳሌ ተጓዳኝ ቋንቋ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:47
msgid ""
"**Show Location Forecast Attribution**: Check this box to show the "
"attribution for the location forecast data, if you are pulling forecast data"
" from [YR.no](https://yr.no/) api. By default, this is disabled."
msgstr ""
"**የመገኛ አካባቢ ትንበያ ባህሪን አሳይ**፡ የትንበያ መረጃን ከ[YR.no](https://yr.no/) api እየጎተቱ "
"ከሆነ የአካባቢ ትንበያ ውሂብን ባህሪ ለማሳየት በዚህ ሳጥን ላይ ምልክት ያድርጉ። በነባሪ፣ ይህ ተሰናክሏል።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:49
msgid ""
"**Location Forecast date display format**: This is the format in which the "
"date will be displayed on the map for the location forecast layer. You can "
"select the correct format from the dropdown list."
msgstr ""
"**የቦታ ትንበያ ቀን ማሳያ ቅርጸት**፡ ይህ ቀኑ በካርታው ላይ ለአካባቢ ትንበያ ንብርብር የሚታይበት ቅርጸት ነው። "
"ከተቆልቋዩ ዝርዝር ውስጥ ትክክለኛውን ቅርጸት መምረጥ ይችላሉ."

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:51
msgid ""
"**Cluster Location Forecast Points**: Check this box to cluster the location"
" forecast points on the map. This is useful if you have a large number of "
"location forecast points and want to reduce the clutter on the map. By "
"default, this is disabled."
msgstr ""
"**የክላስተር አካባቢ ትንበያ ነጥቦች**፡ በካርታው ላይ የአካባቢ ትንበያ ነጥቦችን ለመሰብሰብ በዚህ ሳጥን ላይ ምልክት "
"ያድርጉ። ይህ ብዙ ቁጥር ያላቸው የአካባቢ ትንበያ ነጥቦች ካሉዎት እና በካርታው ላይ ያለውን የተዝረከረከ ሁኔታ ለመቀነስ"
" ከፈለጉ ጠቃሚ ነው። በነባሪ፣ ይህ ተሰናክሏል።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:54
msgid ""
"**Cluster Minimum number of points**: This is the minimum number of points "
"required to cluster the location forecast points on the map. By default, it "
"is set to `2`. You can change it to a value that works best for your number "
"of locations."
msgstr ""
"**ክላስተር ዝቅተኛው የነጥቦች ብዛት**፡ ይህ በካርታው ላይ ያለውን የአካባቢ ትንበያ ነጥቦችን ለመሰብሰብ የሚያስፈልገው"
" ዝቅተኛው የነጥቦች ብዛት ነው። በነባሪነት ወደ `2` ተቀናብሯል። ለእርስዎ የአካባቢ ብዛት በተሻለ ወደሚሰራ እሴት "
"ሊለውጡት ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:57
msgid ""
"**Cluster Radius**: This is the radius in pixels for clustering the location"
" forecast points on the map. By default, it is set to `50`. You can change "
"it to a value that works best for your number of locations."
msgstr ""
"** ክላስተር ራዲየስ ***: ይህ በካርታው ላይ ያሉ የአካባቢ ትንበያ ነጥቦችን ለመሰብሰብ በፒክሰሎች ውስጥ ያለው "
"ራዲየስ ነው። በነባሪነት ወደ `50` ተቀናብሯል። ለእርስዎ የአካባቢ ብዛት በተሻለ ወደሚሰራ እሴት ሊለውጡት ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:60
msgid ""
"Clustering is a technique used to group similar points together on the map "
"to reduce clutter and improve the user experience. When clustering is "
"enabled, the map will show a single point for a group of points that are "
"close to each other. When the user zooms in, the points will be expanded to "
"show the individual points. This is useful when you have a large number of "
"points on the map and want to reduce the clutter. However, it can also make "
"it difficult to see individual points when zoomed out. You can experiment "
"with the clustering settings to find the best configuration for your map, by"
" adjusting the minimum number of points and the radius for clustering. "
"Continue adjusting these settings until you find a balance between "
"clustering and showing individual points that works best for your map."
msgstr ""
"ክላስተር (Clastering) ተመሳሳይ ነጥቦችን በካርታው ላይ በማሰባሰብ የተዝረከረከ ሁኔታን ለመቀነስ እና የተጠቃሚውን"
" ልምድ ለማሻሻል የሚረዳ ዘዴ ነው። ክላስተር ሲነቃ ካርታው እርስ በርስ የሚቀራረቡ የነጥብ ቡድን አንድ ነጥብ ያሳያል። "
"ተጠቃሚው ሲያሳድግ ነጥቦቹ የተናጠል ነጥቦችን ለማሳየት ነጥቦቹ ይሰፋሉ። ይህ በካርታው ላይ ብዙ ቁጥር ያላቸው ነጥቦች "
"ሲኖሩዎት እና የተዝረከረከውን መጠን ለመቀነስ ሲፈልጉ ጠቃሚ ነው. ሆኖም፣ ሲገለሉ የተናጠል ነጥቦችን ለማየትም አስቸጋሪ "
"ያደርገዋል። አነስተኛውን የነጥቦች ብዛት እና ለክላስተር ራዲየስ በማስተካከል ለካርታዎ ምርጡን ውቅር ለማግኘት በክላስተር"
" ቅንጅቶች መሞከር ይችላሉ። ለካርታዎ በተሻለ ሁኔታ የሚሰሩትን ነጥቦች በማሰባሰብ እና በማሳየት መካከል ሚዛን እስኪያገኙ"
" ድረስ እነዚህን ቅንብሮች ማስተካከልዎን ይቀጥሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:69
msgid "Zoom Locations"
msgstr "ቦታዎችን አጉላ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:71
msgid ""
"Zoom locations are predefined locations on the map that the user can zoom "
"to. This is useful for quickly navigating to common locations on the map, "
"such as the capital city or other important locations. You can add, edit or "
"delete zoom locations, as shown below:"
msgstr ""
"የማጉላት ሥፍራዎች በካርታው ላይ ተጠቃሚው ሊያሳያቸው የሚችላቸው አስቀድሞ የተገለጹ ቦታዎች ናቸው። ይህ በካርታው ላይ "
"ወደሚገኙ የጋራ ቦታዎች እንደ ዋና ከተማ ወይም ሌሎች አስፈላጊ ቦታዎች በፍጥነት ለመጓዝ ይጠቅማል። ከታች እንደሚታየው "
"የማጉላት ቦታዎችን ማከል፣ ማርትዕ ወይም መሰረዝ ይችላሉ፡"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:75
msgid ""
"![Zoom Locations "
"Settings](../../_static/images/settings/homepagemap/zoom_locations.png "
"\"Zoom Locations Settings\")"
msgstr ""
"![የአከባቢ ቅንብሮችን "
"አጉላ](../../_static/images/settings/Homepagemap/zoom_locations.png \"የማጉላት "
"አካባቢዎች ቅንብሮችን\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:75
msgid "Zoom Locations Settings"
msgstr "የአካባቢ ቅንብሮችን አጉላ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:77
msgid ""
"This will be displayed as a dropdown on the map, allowing the user to "
"quickly zoom to the selected location."
msgstr ""
"ይህ በካርታው ላይ ተቆልቋይ ሆኖ ይታያል፣ ይህም ተጠቃሚው ወደ ተመረጠው ቦታ በፍጥነት እንዲያሳድግ ያስችለዋል።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:79
msgid ""
"![Zoom Locations "
"Frontend](../../_static/images/settings/homepagemap/zoom_locations_frontend.png"
" \"Zoom Locations Dropdown\")"
msgstr ""
"![አጉላ ቦታዎች ፊት "
"ለፊት](../../_static/images/settings/Homepagemap/zoom_locations_frontend.png "
"\"የማጉላት ቦታዎች ተቆልቋይ\")"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:79
msgid "Zoom Locations Frontend"
msgstr "አጉላ ቦታዎች Frontend"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:81
msgid "Geomanager Layers"
msgstr "የጂኦማኔጀር ንብርብሮች"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:83
msgid ""
"You can add up to five (5) Geomanager layers to the homepage map. Geomanager"
" layers are custom layers added to Climweb using the Geomanager Module. Once"
" you add layers on Geomanager, they can be added to the homepage map."
msgstr ""
"በመነሻ ገጹ ካርታ ላይ እስከ አምስት (5) የጂኦማኔጀር ንብርብሮችን ማከል ይችላሉ። የጂኦማኔጀር ንብርብሮች የጂኦማኔጀር"
" ሞጁሉን በመጠቀም ወደ Climweb የተጨመሩ ብጁ ንብርብሮች ናቸው። አንዴ ንብርብሮችን በጂኦማኔጀር ላይ ካከሉ በኋላ "
"ወደ መነሻ ገጽ ካርታው ሊጨመሩ ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:86
msgid ""
"To access the Geomanager layers settings, click on the `Geomanager Layers` "
"tab in the homepage map settings."
msgstr ""
"የጂኦማኔጀር የንብርብሮች ቅንብሮችን ለመድረስ በመነሻ ገፅ ካርታ ቅንጅቶች ውስጥ ያለውን የ«ጂኦማኔጀር ንብርብሮች» ትርን"
" ጠቅ ያድርጉ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:88
msgid ""
"![Geomanager Layers "
"Settings](../../_static/images/settings/homepagemap/geomanager_map_layers.png"
" \"Geomanager Layers Settings\")"
msgstr ""
"![Geomanager Layers "
"Settings](.../../_static/images/settings/homepagemap/geomanager_map_layers.png"
" \"Geomanager Layers Settings)\""

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:88
msgid "Geomanager Layers Settings"
msgstr "የጂኦማኔጀር የንብርብሮች ቅንብሮች"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:90
msgid ""
"Clicking on the Plus (+) button will open a popup where you can select the "
"type of Geomanager layer you want to add."
msgstr ""
"የፕላስ (+) ቁልፍን ጠቅ ማድረግ የሚፈልጉትን የጂኦማኔጀር ንብርብር አይነት መምረጥ የሚችሉበት ብቅ ባይ ይከፍታል።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:92
msgid "Currently, you can add the following types of Geomanager layers:"
msgstr "በአሁኑ ጊዜ የሚከተሉትን የጂኦማኔጀር ንብርብሮችን ማከል ይችላሉ:"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:94
msgid "Raster Layer"
msgstr "ራስተር ንብርብር"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:95
msgid "Vector Tile Layer"
msgstr "የቬክተር ንጣፍ ንብርብር"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:96
msgid "WMS Layer"
msgstr "የ WMS ንብርብር"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:98
msgid ""
"Once you select the type of layer, you will be prompted to enter the "
"required information for that layer."
msgstr "አንዴ የንብርብሩን አይነት ከመረጡ ለዚያ ንብርብር አስፈላጊውን መረጃ እንዲያስገቡ ይጠየቃሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:100
msgid ""
"**Choose Layer**: You can click to select the layer you want to add from the"
" list of available layers in Geomanager."
msgstr ""
"**ንብርብርን ምረጥ**፡ በጂኦማኔጀር ከሚገኙት የንብርብሮች ዝርዝር ውስጥ ለመጨመር የሚፈልጉትን ንብርብር ለመምረጥ ጠቅ "
"ማድረግ ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:101
msgid ""
"**Icon**: You can select an icon for the layer that will be displayed on the"
" map"
msgstr "** አዶ ***: በካርታው ላይ ለሚታየው ንብርብር አዶ መምረጥ ይችላሉ"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:102
msgid ""
"**Display Name**: This is the name of the layer that will be displayed on "
"the map. By default, it is set to the name of the layer in Geomanager. You "
"can change it, for example, to the corresponding language of your Climweb "
"Instance."
msgstr ""
"** የማሳያ ስም**፡ ይህ በካርታው ላይ የሚታየው የንብርብር ስም ነው። በነባሪነት በጂኦማኔጀር ውስጥ ወደ የንብርብሩ "
"ስም ተቀናብሯል። ሊለውጡት ይችላሉ፣ ለምሳሌ፣ ወደ የእርስዎ Climweb ምሳሌ ተጓዳኝ ቋንቋ።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:104
msgid ""
"**Enabled**: Check this box to show the layer on the homepage map. By "
"default, this is enabled."
msgstr ""
"** ነቅቷል ***: በመነሻ ገጽ ካርታ ላይ ያለውን ንብርብር ለማሳየት በዚህ ሳጥን ላይ ምልክት ያድርጉ። በነባሪ ይህ "
"ነቅቷል።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:105
msgid ""
"**Show on map by default**: Check this box to show the layer on the map by "
"default. If this is not checked, the layer will not be shown on the map "
"until the user selects it from the layer list. If multiple layers are "
"selected, only the first one will be shown."
msgstr ""
"**በካርታው ላይ በነባሪ አሳይ**፡ በካርታው ላይ ያለውን ንብርብር በነባሪ ለማሳየት በዚህ ሳጥን ላይ ምልክት ያድርጉ። "
"ይህ ካልተረጋገጠ ተጠቃሚው ከንብርብሮች ዝርዝር ውስጥ እስኪመርጥ ድረስ ንብርብሩ በካርታው ላይ አይታይም። ብዙ ንብርብሮች"
" ከተመረጡ, የመጀመሪያው ብቻ ይታያል."

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/homepage-map.md:109
msgid ""
"If you mark a layer as `Show on map by default`, it will be only shown when "
"`Show Location Forecast Layer` or `Show CAP Warnings Layer` are disabled."
msgstr ""
"ንብርብሩን 'በካርታው ላይ በነባሪ አሳይ' ብለው ምልክት ካደረጉት፣ የሚታየው `የአካባቢ ትንበያ ንብርብርን አሳይ' ወይም"
" 'የ CAP ማስጠንቀቂያ ንብርብርን አሳይ' ሲሰናከል ብቻ ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/manage_settings/index.md:1
msgid "Configure Settings"
msgstr "ቅንብሮችን ያዋቅሩ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:1
msgid "Backup and Restore Guide"
msgstr "የመጠባበቂያ እና እነበረበት መልስ መመሪያ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:3
msgid "Backup Mechanism"
msgstr "የመጠባበቂያ ዘዴ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:5
msgid ""
"Climweb uses [django-dbbackup](https://github.com/jazzband/django-dbbackup) "
"for backup and restore of the database and media files. The backup process "
"is scheduled using Celery tasks, and currently runs every midnight."
msgstr ""
"Climweb የውሂብ ጎታውን እና የሚዲያ ፋይሎችን ለመጠባበቅ እና ወደነበረበት ለመመለስ [django-"
"dbbackup](https://github.com/jazzband/django-dbbackup) ይጠቀማል። የመጠባበቂያ ሂደቱ "
"የሴሊሪ ተግባሮችን በመጠቀም የታቀደ ነው, እና በአሁኑ ጊዜ በየእኩለ ሌሊት ይሰራል."

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:8
msgid ""
"The https://django-dbbackup.readthedocs.io/en/stable documentation provides "
"detailed information on how the package works."
msgstr ""
"የ https://django-dbbackup.readthedocs.io/en/stable ዶክመንቴሽን እሽጉ እንዴት እንደሚሰራ "
"ዝርዝር መረጃ ይሰጣል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:11
msgid "Backup Location"
msgstr "የመጠባበቂያ ቦታ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:13
msgid ""
"Currently, the backup files are store in the local filesystem of the server."
" The location is defined in the settings file as below:"
msgstr ""
"በአሁኑ ጊዜ የመጠባበቂያ ፋይሎቹ በአገልጋዩ አካባቢያዊ የፋይል ስርዓት ውስጥ ይከማቻሉ. ቦታው በቅንብሮች ፋይል ውስጥ "
"እንደሚከተለው ይገለጻል፡-"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:23
msgid "DB and Media files restoration"
msgstr "DB እና የሚዲያ ፋይሎችን ወደነበሩበት መመለስ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:25
msgid "The restore process is done using the `dbrestore` management command."
msgstr "የመልሶ ማቋቋም ሂደቱ የሚከናወነው የ‹dbrestore› አስተዳደር ትዕዛዝን በመጠቀም ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:27
msgid ""
"Ensure you have placed your recent backup files in the backup directory. "
"Usually these are two files, the database dump file and media files tar file"
msgstr ""
"የቅርብ ጊዜ የመጠባበቂያ ፋይሎችህን በመጠባበቂያ ማውጫ ውስጥ እንዳስቀመጥክ አረጋግጥ። ብዙውን ጊዜ እነዚህ ሁለት ፋይሎች"
" ናቸው, የውሂብ ጎታ መጣያ ፋይል እና የሚዲያ ፋይሎች ታር ፋይል"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:30
msgid ""
"You need to start with an empty database with PostGIS as the only external "
"extension installed."
msgstr "እንደ ብቸኛው ውጫዊ ቅጥያ በ PostGIS በባዶ ዳታቤዝ መጀመር ያስፈልግዎታል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:32
msgid ""
"If you have extensions like `postgis_topology` or `postgis_tiger_geocoder` "
"installed, you might need to drop these extensions using similar command as "
"below:"
msgstr ""
"እንደ `postgis_topology` ወይም `postgis_tiger_geocoder` የተጫኑ ቅጥያዎች ካሉህ ከታች ያለውን "
"ተመሳሳይ ትዕዛዝ በመጠቀም እነዚህን ቅጥያዎች መጣል ሊኖርብህ ይችላል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/backup-restore.md:42
msgid "Then, you can run the restore command as below:"
msgstr "ከዚያ የመልሶ ማግኛ ትዕዛዙን እንደሚከተለው ማሄድ ይችላሉ-"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/dev.sh.md:1
msgid "./dev.sh"
msgstr "./dev.sh"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/dev.sh.md:3
msgid ""
"dev.sh is a helper bash script which makes working with Climweb’s "
"development environment a breeze."
msgstr "dev.sh ከ Climweb ልማት አካባቢ ጋር አብሮ መስራትን ነፋሻማ የሚያደርግ የረዳት ባሽ ስክሪፕት ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/dev.sh.md:5
msgid ""
"By default, running `./dev.sh` will start the dev env and make sure the "
"containers are running as your actual user."
msgstr ""
"በነባሪነት `./dev.sh`ን ማስኬድ dev envን ይጀምራል እና መያዣዎቹ እንደ ትክክለኛ ተጠቃሚዎ እየሰሩ መሆናቸውን "
"ያረጋግጡ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/dev.sh.md:8
msgid "Examples of `./dev.sh` usage:"
msgstr "የ`./dev.sh` አጠቃቀም ምሳሌዎች፡-"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/dev.sh.md:29
msgid "Why ./dev.sh ensures the containers run as you"
msgstr "ለምን ./dev.sh ኮንቴይነሮቹ እንደ እርስዎ እንዲሄዱ ያረጋግጣል"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/dev.sh.md:31
msgid ""
"In dev mode Climweb's source control directories are mounted from your local"
" git repo into the containers. By mounting these the containers will see "
"source code changes and automatically rebuild. However, if the containers "
"are not running as your actual user then the containers might accidentally "
"change the ownership or create files owned by the user running inside the "
"container. So by running the containers as your user there is no chance that"
" your source control directories will have file ownership problems. "
"Additionally, it is best practice to not run Docker containers as the "
"default root user."
msgstr ""
"በዴቭ ሞድ ውስጥ የClimweb ምንጭ መቆጣጠሪያ ማውጫዎች ከአከባቢዎ ጂት ሪፖ ወደ ኮንቴይነሮች ተጭነዋል። እነዚህን "
"በመጫን ኮንቴይነሮቹ የምንጭ ኮድ ለውጦችን ያያሉ እና በራስ-ሰር እንደገና ይገነባሉ። ነገር ግን ኮንቴይነሮቹ እንደ "
"ትክክለኛ ተጠቃሚዎ የማይሄዱ ከሆኑ ኮንቴይነሮቹ በድንገት የባለቤትነት መብታቸውን ሊለውጡ ወይም በተጠቃሚው ባለቤትነት "
"የተያዙ ፋይሎችን በማጠራቀሚያው ውስጥ ሊሰሩ ይችላሉ። ስለዚህ ኮንቴይነሮችን እንደ ተጠቃሚዎ በማስኬድ የምንጭ መቆጣጠሪያ "
"ማውጫዎችዎ የፋይል ባለቤትነት ችግሮች ሊገጥማቸው የሚችልበት ዕድል የለም። በተጨማሪም የዶከር ኮንቴይነሮችን እንደ ነባሪ "
"ስር ተጠቃሚ አለማድረግ ጥሩ ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:1
msgid "Development tools"
msgstr "የልማት መሳሪያዎች"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:3
msgid "Backend"
msgstr "ጀርባ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:5
msgid "PostgreSQL + PostGIS"
msgstr "PostgreSQL + PostGIS"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:7
msgid "Climweb uses PostgreSQL for persistent storage."
msgstr "Climweb ለቀጣይ ማከማቻ PostgreSQL ይጠቀማል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:9
msgid ""
"PostGIS is an extension to PostgreSQL that adds support for geographic "
"objects"
msgstr "PostGIS ለጂኦግራፊያዊ ነገሮች ድጋፍን የሚጨምር የ PostgreSQL ቅጥያ ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:11
msgid "[https://www.postgresql.org](https://www.postgresql.org)"
msgstr "[https://www.postgresql.org](https://www.postgresql.org)"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:13
msgid "Django + Wagtail CMS"
msgstr "Django + Wagtail CMS"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:15
msgid ""
"At the core of the system we run the Django framework. A popular framework "
"was chosen to lower the barrier of creating custom modules that extend "
"Climweb. We also looked for a batteries included, simple, and proven "
"framework. Django was the obvious choice."
msgstr ""
"በስርዓቱ እምብርት ላይ የጃንጎን ማዕቀፍ እናካሂዳለን. Climwebን የሚያራዝሙ ብጁ ሞጁሎችን የመፍጠር እንቅፋትን "
"ለመቀነስ ታዋቂ ማዕቀፍ ተመርጧል። እንዲሁም የተካተቱትን፣ ቀላል እና የተረጋገጠውን ባትሪዎች ፈልገን ነበር። ጃንጎ ግልጽ"
" ምርጫ ነበር።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:19
msgid "[https://www.djangoproject.com](https://www.djangoproject.com)"
msgstr "[https://www.djangoproject.com](https://www.djangoproject.com)"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:21
msgid ""
"Wagtail is an open-source content management system (CMS) built on top of "
"Django, a popular Python web framework. It's designed to be developer-"
"friendly, flexible, and provide a modern, intuitive editing experience for "
"content creators."
msgstr ""
"Wagtail በጃንጎ ላይ የተገነባ የክፍት ምንጭ የይዘት አስተዳደር ስርዓት (ሲኤምኤስ) ነው፣ ታዋቂው የፓይዘን ድር "
"ማዕቀፍ። ለገንቢ ተስማሚ፣ ተለዋዋጭ እና ለይዘት ፈጣሪዎች ዘመናዊ፣ ሊታወቅ የሚችል የአርትዖት ተሞክሮ ለማቅረብ ነው "
"የተቀየሰው።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:24
msgid ""
"The user interface of the Wagtail Admin and the overall editing experience "
"provided by Wagtail made it a good choice for Climweb, as it allows for easy"
" content creation and management."
msgstr ""
"የWagtail Admin የተጠቃሚ በይነገጽ እና በ Wagtail የቀረበው አጠቃላይ የአርትዖት ልምድ ለ Climweb ጥሩ "
"ምርጫ አድርጎታል፣ ይህም በቀላሉ ይዘት መፍጠር እና ማስተዳደርን ያስችላል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:27
msgid "[https://wagtail.org](https://wagtail.org)"
msgstr "[https://wagtail.org](https://wagtail.org)"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:29
msgid "Django REST framework"
msgstr "Django REST ማዕቀፍ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:31
msgid ""
"To quickly create endpoints, handle external authentication, object "
"serialization, validation, and do many more things we use Django REST "
"Framework."
msgstr ""
"የመጨረሻ ነጥቦችን በፍጥነት ለመፍጠር፣ የውጭ ማረጋገጥን፣ የነገርን ተከታታይነት፣ ማረጋገጥ እና ብዙ ተጨማሪ ነገሮችን በ"
" Django REST Framework እንጠቀማለን።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:34
msgid ""
"[https://www.django-rest-framework.org](https://www.django-rest-"
"framework.org)"
msgstr ""
"[https://www.django-rest-framework.org](https://www.django-rest-"
"framework.org)"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:36
msgid "Internationalization"
msgstr "አለማቀፋዊነት"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:38
msgid ""
"For internationalization (i18n), we leverage Django's built-in support. "
"Django's internationalization framework allows us to easily translate our "
"web application into multiple languages."
msgstr ""
"ለአለምአቀፋዊነት (i18n)፣ የጃንጎን አብሮገነብ ድጋፍ እንጠቀማለን። የጃንጎ አለምአቀፋዊነት ማዕቀፍ የድር "
"መተግበሪያችንን ወደ ብዙ ቋንቋዎች በቀላሉ እንድንተረጉም ያስችለናል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:41
msgid ""
"To use Django's internationalization features, we wrap our text with a "
"special function called `gettext` or `gettext_lazy`. For more information, "
"refer to the [Django Internationalization and Localization "
"documentation](https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/3.2/topics/i18n/)."
msgstr ""
"የጃንጎን አለማቀፋዊ ባህሪያትን ለመጠቀም፣ ጽሑፎቻችንን 'ጌትቴክስት` ወይም `ጌትቴክስት_lazy` በሚባል ልዩ ተግባር "
"እንጠቅሳለን። ለበለጠ መረጃ፣[Django Internationalization and Localization "
"documents](https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/3.2/topics/i18n/) ይመልከቱ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:46
msgid "Frontend"
msgstr "የፊት ለፊት"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:48
msgid ""
"Climweb mostly uses Django templates for the frontend. However, we also use "
"`Vue.js` for some parts of the frontend that require more interactivity, "
"such as the home page map component."
msgstr ""
"Climweb በአብዛኛው የጃንጎ አብነቶችን ለፊት ለፊት ይጠቀማል። ነገር ግን፣ እንደ መነሻ ገጽ ካርታ አካል ለመሳሰሉት "
"የፊት ለፊት ክፍል አንዳንድ ክፍሎች 'Vue.js'ን እንጠቀማለን።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:51
msgid ""
"We use a custom approach to integrate Vue.js with Django. This approach "
"combines the strengths of Django's templating system with Vue's reactive "
"components and is summarized as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Vue.jsን ከጃንጎ ጋር ለማዋሃድ ብጁ አቀራረብን እንጠቀማለን። ይህ አካሄድ የጃንጎን ቴምፕሊንግ ሲስተም ከ Vue ምላሽ"
" ሰጪ አካላት ጋር በማጣመር እንደሚከተለው ቀርቧል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:54
msgid "**Key steps in the integration of Vue into Django/Wagtail:**"
msgstr "**Vue ወደ Django/Wagtail ውህደት ውስጥ ቁልፍ እርምጃዎች:**"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:56
msgid ""
"**Vue Project Setup**: Use Vite to scaffold a Vue project within the Django "
"project directory, enabling modern JavaScript development with features like"
" hot module replacement."
msgstr ""
"**Vue Project Setup**፡ ዘመናዊ የጃቫስክሪፕት ልማትን እንደ ትኩስ ሞጁል መተካት ያሉ ባህሪያትን በማስቻል "
"የVueን ፕሮጀክት በDjango የፕሮጀክት ማውጫ ውስጥ ለመቅረጽ Viteን ይጠቀሙ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:59
msgid ""
"**Django Template Integration**: Embed Vue components directly into Django "
"templates by adding a <div id=\"app\"></div> and including the Vue "
"application's script via a <script type=\"module\"> tag pointing to the Vite"
" dev server."
msgstr ""
"**የጃንጎ አብነት ውህደት**፡ የVue አካላትን በቀጥታ ወደ Django አብነቶች ክተት <div "
"id=\"app\"></div> በማከል እና የVue መተግበሪያን ስክሪፕት በ<script type=\"module\">ቪት ዴቭ "
"አገልጋይ የሚያመለክት መለያ በማካተት።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:62
msgid ""
"**Development Workflow:** Leverage Vite's development server for rapid "
"development and testing, allowing real-time updates to Vue components "
"without full page reloads."
msgstr ""
"**የልማት የስራ ፍሰት፡** የViteን ልማት አገልጋይ ለፈጣን እድገት እና ለሙከራ መጠቀም፣ ያለሙሉ ገጽ ዳግም መጫን "
"ለVue ክፍሎች በቅጽበት ማሻሻያ ማድረግ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:65
msgid ""
"**Production Build**: Configure Vite to output a production-ready build, and"
" adjust Django's static files settings to serve the compiled assets "
"appropriately."
msgstr ""
"** የምርት ግንባታ ***: ለምርት ዝግጁ የሆነ ግንባታ ለማውጣት Viteን ያዋቅሩ እና የተቀናጁ ንብረቶችን በአግባቡ "
"ለማገልገል የጃንጎን የማይንቀሳቀሱ ፋይሎች ቅንጅቶችን ያስተካክሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:68
msgid ""
"**State Management:** Incorporate Pinia for state management within Vue "
"components, facilitating organized and maintainable application state."
msgstr ""
"**የስቴት አስተዳደር፡** የተደራጀ እና ሊቆይ የሚችል የመተግበሪያ ሁኔታን በማመቻቸት ፒኒያን ለግዛት አስተዳደር በVue"
" ክፍሎች ውስጥ አካትት።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:71
msgid ""
"This integration strategy enables us to enhance our templates with dynamic "
"Vue components while maintaining the benefits of Django's server-side "
"rendering and template system."
msgstr ""
"ይህ የውህደት ስልት የጃንጎን የአገልጋይ ጎን አተረጓጎም እና የአብነት ስርዓትን ጥቅሞች እየጠበቅን የእኛን አብነቶች "
"በተለዋዋጭ የVue ክፍሎች እንድናሻሽል ያስችለናል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:74
msgid ""
"The approach is explained in details "
"[here](https://ilikerobots.medium.com/django-vue-vite-rest-not-required-"
"ca63cfa558fd)"
msgstr ""
"አቀራረቡ በዝርዝር ተብራርቷል [እዚህ](https://ilikerobots.medium.com/django-vue-vite-"
"rest-not-required-ca63cfa558fd)"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:77
msgid "Icons"
msgstr "አዶዎች"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:79
msgid ""
"We mostly use Font Awesome for SVG icons. Font Awesome is a popular icon "
"library that provides a wide range of scalable vector icons. We use "
"[wagtail-font-awesome-svg](https://github.com/wagtail-nest/wagtail-font-"
"awesome-svg), a Wagtail package that allows us to use Font Awesome icons in "
"Wagtail projects."
msgstr ""
"ለSVG አዶዎች ብዙ ጊዜ የምንጠቀመው Font Awesome ነው። ቅርጸ-ቁምፊ ግሩም ሰፊ የቬክተር አዶዎችን የሚያቀርብ "
"ታዋቂ አዶ ቤተ-መጽሐፍት ነው። በ Wagtail ፕሮጀክቶች ውስጥ የፊደል ግሩም አዶዎችን እንድንጠቀም የሚፈቅድ "
"የWagtail ጥቅል [wagtail-font-awesome-svg](https://github.com/wagtail-"
"nest/wagtail-font-awesome-svg) እንጠቀማለን።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/development-tools.md:83
msgid "[https://fontawesome.com](https://fontawesome.com)"
msgstr "[https://fontawesome.com](https://fontawesome.com)"

