msgstr "ለቀጣይ የውሂብ ጎታ ውሂብ የተጫነ የዶክ የድምጽ መጠን ዱካ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_SITE_NAME"
msgstr "CMS_SITE_NAME"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"The human-readable name of your Wagtail installation which welcomes users "
"upon login to the Wagtail admin."
msgstr "ወደ Wagtail አስተዳዳሪ ሲገቡ ተጠቃሚዎችን የሚቀበል የWagtail ጭነት በሰው ሊነበብ የሚችል ስም።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_ADMIN_URL_PATH"
msgstr "CMS_ADMIN_URL_PATH"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Base Path to admin pages. Do not use `admin` or an easy to guess path. "
"Should be one word and can include an hyphen. DO NOT include any slashes at "
"the start or the end."
msgstr ""
"ወደ የአስተዳዳሪ ገፆች የመሠረት መንገድ። 'አስተዳዳሪ' ወይም ለመገመት ቀላል መንገድ አይጠቀሙ። አንድ ቃል መሆን "
"አለበት እና ሰረዝን ሊያካትት ይችላል። በጅማሬም ሆነ በመጨረሻው ላይ ማናቸውንም መቆራረጦች አያካትቱ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_DEBUG"
msgstr "CMS_DEBUG"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"A boolean that turns on/off debug mode. Never deploy a site into production "
"with DEBUG turned on"
msgstr "የስህተት ማረም ሁነታን የሚያበራ/ያጠፋ ቡሊያን። DEBUG በርቶ አንድ ጣቢያ ወደ ምርት በጭራሽ አያሰማራ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "NO"
msgstr "አይ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "False"
msgstr "ውሸት"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_PORT"
msgstr "CMS_PORT"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "Port to run cms"
msgstr "ሴሜ ለማሄድ ወደብ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "80"
msgstr "80"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_BASE_URL"
msgstr "CMS_BASE_URL"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"This is the base URL used by the Wagtail admin site. It is typically used "
"for generating URLs to include in notification emails."
msgstr ""
"ይህ በWagtail አስተዳዳሪ ጣቢያ ጥቅም ላይ የዋለው የመነሻ ዩአርኤል ነው። እሱ በተለምዶ በማሳወቂያ ኢሜይሎች ውስጥ "
"የሚካተቱ ዩአርኤሎችን ለማምረት ያገለግላል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE_CODE"
msgstr "CMS_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE_CODE"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"The language code for the CMS. Availabe codes are `en` for English, `fr` "
"from French, `ar` for Arabic, `am` for Amharic, `es` for Spanish, `sw` for "
"Swahili. Default is `en` if not set"
msgstr ""
"ለሲኤምኤስ የቋንቋ ኮድ። Availabe ኮዶች 'en' ለ እንግሊዝኛ፣ `fr` ከፈረንሳይኛ፣ `ar` ለአረብኛ፣ `am` "
"ለአማርኛ፣ `es` ለስፓኒሽ፣ `sw` ለ ስዋሂሊ ናቸው። ካልተዋቀረ ነባሪው `en` ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "en"
msgstr "እ.ኤ.አ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CSRF_TRUSTED_ORIGINS"
msgstr "CSRF_TRUSTED_ORIGINS"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"This variable can be set when CMS_PORT is not 80 e.g if CMS_PORT=8000, "
"CSRF_TRUSTED_ORIGINS would be the following: http://{YOUR_IP_ADDRESS}:8000, "
"http://{YOUR_IP_ADDRESS}, http://localhost:8000 and http://127.0.0.1:8000"
msgstr ""
"ይህ ተለዋዋጭ CMS_PORT 80 ካልሆነ ሊዋቀር ይችላል ለምሳሌ CMS_PORT=8000 ከሆነ "
"CSRF_TRUSTED_ORIGINS የሚከተለው ይሆናል፡ http://{YOUR_IP_ADDRESS}:8000፣ "
"http://{YOUR_IP_ADDRESS}፣ http://localhost:8000 እና http://127.000."

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "TIME_ZONE"
msgstr "TIME_ZONE"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"A string representing the time zone for this installation. See the [list of "
"time zones](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_tz_database_time_zones). "
"Set this to your country timezone"
msgstr ""
"ለዚህ ጭነት የሰዓት ዞንን የሚወክል ሕብረቁምፊ። [የሰዓት ሰቆች "
"ዝርዝር](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_tz_database_time_zones) ይመልከቱ። "
"ይህንን ወደ አገርዎ የሰዓት ሰቅ ያቀናብሩት።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "UTC"
msgstr "ዩቲሲ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"[List of tz database time "
"zones](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_tz_database_time_zones)"
msgstr ""
"[የ tz ዳታቤዝ የሰዓት ሰቆች "
"ዝርዝር](https://am.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_tz_database_time_zones)"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SECRET_KEY"
msgstr "SECRET_KEY"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"A secret key for a particular Django installation. This is used to provide "
"cryptographic signing, and should be set to a unique, unpredictable value. "
"Django will refuse to start if SECRET_KEY is not set"
msgstr ""
"ለአንድ የተወሰነ የጃንጎ ጭነት ሚስጥራዊ ቁልፍ። ይህ ክሪፕቶግራፊክ ፊርማ ለማቅረብ ጥቅም ላይ ይውላል፣ እና ወደ ልዩ፣ "
"ወደማይታወቅ እሴት መቀናበር አለበት። SECRET_KEY ካልተዋቀረ Django ለመጀመር ፈቃደኛ አይሆንም"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"You can use this online tool [https://djecrety.ir](https://djecrety.ir/) to "
"generate the key and paste"
msgstr ""
"ቁልፉን ለማመንጨት እና ለመለጠፍ ይህን የመስመር ላይ መሳሪያ "
"[https://djecrety.ir](https://djecrety.ir/) መጠቀም ትችላለህ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "ALLOWED_HOSTS"
msgstr "የተፈቀደላቸው_ሆስቶች"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"A list of strings representing the host/domain names that this Django site "
"can serve. This is a security measure to prevent HTTP Host header attacks, "
"which are possible even under many seemingly-safe web server configurations."
msgstr ""
"ይህ የጃንጎ ጣቢያ የሚያገለግለው የአስተናጋጅ/የጎራ ስሞችን የሚወክሉ የሕብረቁምፊዎች ዝርዝር። ይህ የኤችቲቲፒ አስተናጋጅ"
" ራስጌ ጥቃቶችን ለመከላከል የደህንነት እርምጃ ነው፣ይህም ደህንነቱ የተጠበቀ በሚመስሉ የድር አገልጋይ አወቃቀሮች ስር "
"ሊሆን ይችላል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"[Django Allowed "
"Hosts](https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/4.2/ref/settings/#std-setting-"
"ALLOWED_HOSTS)"
msgstr ""
"[Django የተፈቀዱ "
"አስተናጋጆች](https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/4.2/ref/settings/#std-setting-"
"ALLOWED_HOSTS)"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "The host to use for sending email"
msgstr "ኢሜል ለመላክ የሚጠቀምበት አስተናጋጅ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_PORT"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_PORT"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "Port to use for the SMTP server defined in `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`"
msgstr "በ `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST` ውስጥ ለተገለፀው የSMTP አገልጋይ የሚጠቅም ወደብ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "25"
msgstr "25"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_USE_TLS"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_USE_TLS"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Whether to use a TLS (secure) connection when talking to the SMTP server. "
"This is used for explicit TLS connections, generally on port 587"
msgstr ""
"ከSMTP አገልጋይ ጋር በሚነጋገሩበት ጊዜ የቲኤልኤስ (አስተማማኝ) ግንኙነት መጠቀም አለመቻል። ይህ ለ TLS ግንኙነቶች"
" በአጠቃላይ በፖርት 587 ላይ ጥቅም ላይ ይውላል"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "True"
msgstr "እውነት ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_USER"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_USER"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Username to use for the SMTP server defined in `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`. If empty, "
"Django won’t attempt authentication."
msgstr ""
"በ `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST` ውስጥ ለተገለፀው የSMTP አገልጋይ ለመጠቀም የተጠቃሚ ስም። ባዶ ከሆነ፣ Django "
"ለማረጋገጥ አይሞክርም።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD"
msgstr "SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Password to use for the SMTP server defined in `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST`. This "
"setting is used in conjunction with `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_USER` when "
"authenticating to the SMTP server. If either of these settings is empty, "
"Django won’t attempt authentication."
msgstr ""
"በ `SMTP_EMAIL_HOST` ውስጥ ለተገለፀው የSMTP አገልጋይ የሚጠቀሙበት የይለፍ ቃል። ይህ ቅንብር ለSMTP "
"አገልጋዩ ሲረጋገጥ ከ`SMTP_EMAIL_HOST_USER` ጋር በጥምረት ጥቅም ላይ ይውላል። ከእነዚህ ቅንብሮች ውስጥ "
"አንዳቸውም ባዶ ከሆኑ Django ማረጋገጥን አይሞክርም።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_ADMINS"
msgstr "CMS_ADMINS"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"A list of all the people who get code error notifications, in format `\"Name"
" <name@example.com>, Another Name <another@example.com>\"`"
msgstr ""
"የኮድ ስህተት ማሳወቂያዎችን የሚያገኙ ሰዎች ዝርዝር በ`\"ስም <name@example.com>፣ ሌላ ስም "
"<another@example.com>\""

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "DEFAULT_FROM_EMAIL"
msgstr "DEFAULT_FROM_EMAIL"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Default email address to use for various automated correspondence from the "
"site manager(s)"
msgstr "ነባሪ የኢሜይል አድራሻ ከጣቢያ አስተዳዳሪ(ዎች) ለተለያዩ አውቶማቲክ መልእክቶች ለመጠቀም"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "RECAPTCHA_PUBLIC_KEY"
msgstr "RECAPTCHA_PUBLIC_KEY"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Google Recaptcha Public Key. https://www.google.com/recaptcha/about/ will "
"need a Google account for RECAPTCHA_PRIVATE_KEY and RECAPTCHA_PUBLIC_KEY "
"creation"
msgstr ""
"Google Recaptcha ይፋዊ ቁልፍ። https://www.google.com/recaptcha/about/ "
"ለRECAPTCHA_PRIVATE_KEY እና RECAPTCHA_PUBLIC_KEY መፍጠር የጎግል መለያ ያስፈልገዋል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "RECAPTCHA_PRIVATE_KEY"
msgstr "RECAPTCHA_PRIVATE_KEY"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "Google Recaptcha Private Key"
msgstr "Google Recaptcha የግል ቁልፍ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_NUM_OF_WORKERS"
msgstr "CMS_NUM_OF_WORKERS"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"Gunicorn number of workers. Recommended value should be `(2 x $num_cores) + "
"1 `. For example, if your server has `4 CPU Cores`, this value should be set"
" to `9`, which is the result of `(2 x 4) + 1 = 9`"
msgstr ""
"የጉኒኮርን ሠራተኞች ብዛት። የሚመከር እሴት `(2 x $num_cores) + 1 ` መሆን አለበት። ለምሳሌ፣ አገልጋይህ "
"`4 CPU Cores` ካለው፣ ይህ ዋጋ ወደ `9` መቀናበር አለበት፣ ይህም የ`(2 x 4) + 1 = 9` ውጤት ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"[Gunicorn Workers "
"details](https://docs.gunicorn.org/en/latest/design.html#how-many-workers)"
msgstr ""
"[የጉኒኮርን ሠራተኞች ዝርዝሮች](https://docs.gunicorn.org/en/latest/design.html#how-"
"many-workers)"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_STATIC_VOLUME"
msgstr "CMS_STATIC_ድምጽ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "Mounted docker volume path for persisting CMS static files"
msgstr "ለተከታታይ የCMS የማይንቀሳቀሱ ፋይሎች የተገጠመ የዶክ የድምጽ መጠን ዱካ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "./climeb/static"
msgstr "./climeb/static"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_MEDIA_VOLUME"
msgstr "CMS_MEDIA_ድምጽ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "Mounted docker volume path for persisting CMS media files"
msgstr "ለተከታታይ የCMS ሚዲያ ፋይሎች የተገጠመ የዶከር ድምጽ ዱካ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "./climeb/media"
msgstr "./climeb/ሚዲያ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "CMS_UPGRADE_HOOK_URL"
msgstr "CMS_UPGRADE_HOOK_URL"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"[Webhook](https://github.com/adnanh/webhook) url to your server that "
"triggers a cms upgrade script"
msgstr ""
"[Webhook](https://github.com/adnanh/webhook) ሴሜ ማሻሻያ ስክሪፕት ወደሚያመጣ ዩአርኤል ወደ "
"አገልጋይህ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "BACKUP_VOLUME"
msgstr "BACKUP_VOLUME"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "Mounted docker volume path for persisting Backup dp and media files"
msgstr "ለቀጣይ የመጠባበቂያ ዲፒ እና የሚዲያ ፋይሎች የተገጠመ የዶከር ድምጽ መንገድ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "./climeb/backup"
msgstr "./climeb/መጠባበቂያ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "WAGTAIL_NEWSLETTER_MAILCHIMP_API_KEY"
msgstr "WAGTAIL_NEWSLETTER_MAILCHIMP_API_KEY"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"When using the default Mailchimp backend, this setting specifies the API "
"key. An API key can be obtained from the [Mailchimp "
"website](https://us1.admin.mailchimp.com/account/api)."
msgstr ""
"ነባሪውን የMailchimp backend ሲጠቀሙ ይህ ቅንብር የኤፒአይ ቁልፉን ይገልጻል። የኤፒአይ ቁልፍ "
"ከ[Mailchimp ድህረ ገጽ](https://us1.admin.mailchimp.com/account/api) ማግኘት ይቻላል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "WAGTAIL_NEWSLETTER_FROM_NAME"
msgstr "WAGTAIL_NEWSLETTER_FROM_NAME"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"When sending a newsletter, this value will appear as the email sender’s "
"name."
msgstr "ጋዜጣ ሲላክ ይህ ዋጋ እንደ ኢሜል ላኪው ስም ሆኖ ይታያል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid "WAGTAIL_NEWSLETTER_REPLY_TO"
msgstr "WAGTAIL_NEWSLETTER_REPLY_TO"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/environmental-variables.md
msgid ""
"When sending a newsletter, this value will appear as the email sender’s "
"address. Be sure to configure your email domain to allow the newsletter "
"service to send emails on behalf of this address, otherwise they will likely"
" be marked as spam."
msgstr ""
"ጋዜጣ ሲላክ ይህ ዋጋ እንደ ኢሜል ላኪ አድራሻ ሆኖ ይታያል። የዜና መጽሔቱ አገልግሎት ይህን አድራሻ ወክሎ ኢሜይሎችን "
"እንዲልክ ለመፍቀድ የኢሜል ጎራዎን ማዋቀርዎን እርግጠኛ ይሁኑ፣ ካልሆነ ግን እንደ አይፈለጌ መልዕክት ምልክት ሊደረግባቸው"
" ይችላል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/index.md:1
msgid "Development"
msgstr "ልማት"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/index.md:3
msgid ""
"The dev environment runs Climweb services with source code hot reloading "
"enabled. It also runs the django server in development modes. It is "
"recommended that you use `dev.sh` found in the root of the Climweb repo."
msgstr ""
"የዴቭ አካባቢው የClimweb አገልግሎቶችን የምንጭ ኮድ ትኩስ ዳግም መጫን የነቃ ነው። እንዲሁም django አገልጋይን "
"በልማት ሁነታዎች ውስጥ ይሰራል። በ Climweb repo ስር የሚገኘውን `dev.sh`ን እንዲጠቀሙ ይመከራል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:1
msgid "Running the dev environment"
msgstr "የዴቭ አካባቢን በማሄድ ላይ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:3
msgid ""
"If you want to contribute to Climweb you need to setup the development "
"environment on your local computer. The best way to do this is via Docker "
"compose so that you can start the app with the least amount of hassle."
msgstr ""
"ለ Climweb አስተዋፅዖ ማድረግ ከፈለጉ በአከባቢዎ ኮምፒውተር ላይ ያለውን የእድገት አካባቢ ማዋቀር ያስፈልግዎታል። "
"ይህን ለማድረግ በጣም ጥሩው መንገድ በ Docker compose በኩል መተግበሪያውን በትንሹ ጣጣ መጀመር ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:7
msgid ""
"For production deployment, please visit [https://github.com/wmo-raf/climweb-"
"docker](https://github.com/wmo-raf/climweb-docker)"
msgstr ""
"ለምርት ማሰማራት፣ እባክዎን [https://github.com/wmo-raf/climweb-"
"docker](https://github.com/wmo-raf/climweb-docker) ይጎብኙ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:10
msgid "Cloning the repository"
msgstr "ማከማቻውን መዝጋት"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:12
msgid ""
"The first step is to clone the Climweb repository from GitHub. You can do "
"this by running the following command in your terminal:"
msgstr ""
"የመጀመሪያው እርምጃ የClimweb ማከማቻውን ከ GitHub መዝጋት ነው። በተርሚናልዎ ውስጥ የሚከተለውን ትዕዛዝ በማሄድ"
" ይህንን ማድረግ ይችላሉ-"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:20
msgid "Create `.env` file"
msgstr "የ`.env` ፋይል ይፍጠሩ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:22
msgid ""
"Next, you need to create an environment file that contains the necessary "
"configuration for the development environment. You can do this by copying "
"the sample dev environment file provided in the repository:"
msgstr ""
"በመቀጠል ለልማት አካባቢ አስፈላጊውን ውቅር የያዘ የአካባቢ ፋይል መፍጠር ያስፈልግዎታል. በማጠራቀሚያው ውስጥ የቀረበውን"
" የናሙና ዲቪ አካባቢ ፋይል በመቅዳት ይህንን ማድረግ ይችላሉ፡-"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:29
msgid ""
"Update the `.env` file with the required configuration. See the Environment "
"Variables section for reference on the available environment variables and "
"their descriptions."
msgstr ""
"የ`.env` ፋይልን በሚፈለገው ውቅር ያዘምኑ። ያሉትን የአካባቢ ተለዋዋጮች እና መግለጫዎቻቸውን ለማጣቀሻ የአካባቢ "
"ተለዋዋጮች ክፍልን ይመልከቱ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:32
msgid "Quickstart"
msgstr "ፈጣን ጅምር"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:34
msgid ""
"If you are familiar with git and Docker Compose run these commands to launch"
" Climweb’s dev environment locally, otherwise please start from the "
"Installing Requirements section below."
msgstr ""
"Git እና Docker Compose የሚያውቁት ከሆነ የClimweb's dev አካባቢን በአገር ውስጥ ለማስጀመር እነዚህን "
"ትዕዛዞች ያሂዱ፣ ካልሆነ እባክዎን ከታች ካለው የመጫኛ መስፈርቶች ክፍል ይጀምሩ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:51
msgid "Installing requirements"
msgstr "የመጫኛ መስፈርቶች"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:53
msgid ""
"If you haven’t already installed docker and Docker Compose on your computer "
"you can do so by following the instructions on "
"[https://docs.docker.com/desktop](https://docs.docker.com/desktop) and "
"[https://docs.docker.com/compose/install](https://docs.docker.com/compose/install)"
msgstr ""
"አስቀድመህ በኮምፒውተርህ ላይ ዶከር እና ዶከር አዘጋጅን ካልጫንክ "
"በ[https://docs.docker.com/desktop](https://docs.docker.com/desktop) እና "
"[https://docs.docker.com/compose/install](https://docs.docker.com/compose/install)"
" ላይ ያሉትን መመሪያዎች በመከተል ማድረግ ትችላለህ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:58
msgid ""
"Docker version 19.03 is the minimum required to build Climweb. It is "
"strongly advised however that you install the latest version of Docker "
"available. Please check that your docker is up to date by running `docker "
"-v`."
msgstr ""
"ክሊምዌብን ለመገንባት Docker ስሪት 19.03 ዝቅተኛው የሚያስፈልገው ነው። ነገር ግን የቅርብ ጊዜውን የዶከር ስሪት "
"እንዲጭኑ በጥብቅ ይመከራል። እባኮትን `docker -v`ን በማሄድ ዶከርዎ የተዘመነ መሆኑን ያረጋግጡ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:62
msgid ""
"You will also need git installed which you can do by following the "
"instructions on [https://www.linode.com/docs/development/version-"
"control/how-to-install-git-on-linux-mac-and-"
"windows](https://www.linode.com/docs/development/version-control/how-to-"
"install-git-on-linux-mac-and-windows)."
msgstr ""
"እንዲሁም በ[https://www.linode.com/docs/development/version-control/how-to-"
"install-git-on-linux-mac-and-"
"windows](https://www.linode.com/docs/development/version-control/how-to-"
"install-git-dows-and-windows) ላይ በመከተል ሊያደርጉት የሚችሉት git መጫን ያስፈልግዎታል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:65
msgid ""
"Once you have finished installing all the required software you should be "
"able to run the following commands in your terminal."
msgstr "ሁሉንም አስፈላጊ ሶፍትዌሮች ከጫኑ በኋላ የሚከተሉትን ትዕዛዞች በተርሚናልዎ ውስጥ ማስኬድ አለብዎት።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:78
msgid ""
"If all commands return something similar as described in the example, then "
"you are ready to proceed!"
msgstr "ሁሉም ትዕዛዞች በምሳሌው ላይ እንደተገለጸው ተመሳሳይ ነገር ከመለሱ፣ ለመቀጠል ዝግጁ ነዎት!"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:80
msgid "Starting the development environment"
msgstr "የልማት አካባቢን መጀመር"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:82
msgid ""
"First, you need to clone the repository. Execute the following commands to "
"clone the main branch. If you are not familiar with git clone, this will "
"download a copy of Climweb’s code to your computer."
msgstr ""
"በመጀመሪያ, ማከማቻውን መዝጋት ያስፈልግዎታል. ዋናውን ቅርንጫፍ ለመዝጋት የሚከተሉትን ትዕዛዞችን ያከናውኑ። ስለ git "
"clone የማያውቁት ከሆነ፣ ይህ የClimweb ኮድ ቅጂ ወደ ኮምፒውተርዎ ያወርዳል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:92
msgid ""
"Now that we have our copy of the repo and have changed directories to the "
"newly created climweb, we can bring up the containers."
msgstr ""
"አሁን የኛን ሪፖ ቅጂ አግኝተናል እና ማውጫዎችን ወደ አዲስ የተፈጠረ ክሊምዌብ ቀይረናል፣ እቃዎቹን ማምጣት እንችላለን።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:95
msgid ""
"If you do not want to use the provided `dev.sh` script, you can run the "
"following command to start the development environment:"
msgstr ""
"የቀረበውን `dev.sh` ስክሪፕት ለመጠቀም ካልፈለጉ፣ የእድገት አካባቢውን ለመጀመር የሚከተለውን ትዕዛዝ ማሄድ ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:103
msgid ""
"Note that the `docker-compose.dev.yml` file is used to override the default "
"`docker-compose.yml` file with development specific settings."
msgstr ""
"የ`docker-compose.dev.yml` ፋይል ነባሪውን `docker-compose.yml` ፋይል ከግንባታ ልዩ ቅንጅቶች "
"ጋር ለመሻር ጥቅም ላይ እንደሚውል ልብ ይበሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:107
msgid "Accessing the web application"
msgstr "የድር መተግበሪያን መድረስ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:109
msgid ""
"Once the containers are up and running, you can access the Climweb "
"application in your web browser at "
"[http://localhost:8000](http://localhost:8000). The port can be changed in "
"the `.env` file if needed by modifying the `CLIMWEB_DEV_PORT` variable."
msgstr ""
"ኮንቴይነሮቹ አንዴ ከሰሩ እና ሲሰሩ የClimweb መተግበሪያን በድር አሳሽዎ ውስጥ "
"በ[http://localhost:8000](http://localhost:8000) ማግኘት ይችላሉ። አስፈላጊ ከሆነ "
"የ`CLIMWEB_DEV_PORT` ተለዋዋጭን በማሻሻል ወደቡ በ`.env` ፋይል ውስጥ ሊቀየር ይችላል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:114
msgid "Creating a superuser"
msgstr "ሱፐር ተጠቃሚ መፍጠር"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:116
msgid ""
"To create a superuser for the Climweb application, you can run the following"
" command in a separate terminal window:"
msgstr ""
"ለ Climweb መተግበሪያ ሱፐር ተጠቃሚ ለመፍጠር፣ የሚከተለውን ትዕዛዝ በተለየ ተርሚናል መስኮት ማሄድ ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:122
msgid "Keep the container running"
msgstr "መያዣው እንዲሠራ ያድርጉት"

#: ../../_docs/technical/development/running-dev-environment.md:124
msgid ""
"The containers need to keep running while you are developing. They also "
"monitor file changes and update automatically, so you don’t need to worry "
"about reloading. Any change to the code will trigger a reload and you can "
"see the changes immediately."
msgstr ""
"በማደግ ላይ እያሉ መያዣዎቹ መሮጥ አለባቸው። እንዲሁም የፋይል ለውጦችን ይቆጣጠራሉ እና በራስ-ሰር ያዘምኑ፣ ስለዚህ "
"እንደገና ስለ መጫን መጨነቅ አያስፈልገዎትም። በኮዱ ላይ የሚደረግ ማንኛውም ለውጥ ዳግም መጫንን ያስነሳል እና ለውጦቹን "
"ወዲያውኑ ማየት ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:1
msgid "Creating a Plugin"
msgstr "ፕለጊን መፍጠር"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:3
msgid ""
"In this guide we will dive into how to create a Climweb plugin, discuss the "
"plugin architecture and give an example plugin to get inspiration from and "
"discuss how to publish your plugin."
msgstr ""
"በዚህ መመሪያ ውስጥ እንዴት የ Climweb ፕለጊን መፍጠር እንደምንችል፣ ስለ ፕለጊን አርክቴክቸር እንወያይ እና አንድ "
"ምሳሌ ተሰኪን እንሰጣለን እና እንዴት ተሰኪዎን ማተም እንደሚችሉ እንወያያለን።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:6
msgid "Plugin Architecture"
msgstr "ተሰኪ አርክቴክቸር"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:8
msgid ""
"A ClimWeb Plugin is fundamentally a folder named after the plugin. The "
"folder should be a [Django/Wagtail "
"App](https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/5.1/ref/applications/)"
msgstr ""
"ClimWeb Plugin በመሠረቱ በተሰኪው ስም የተሰየመ አቃፊ ነው። አቃፊው [Django/Wagtail "
"መተግበሪያ](https://docs.djangoproject.com/en/5.1/ref/applications/) መሆን አለበት።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:11
msgid "Initialize your plugin from the plugin template"
msgstr "ተሰኪዎን ከተሰኪው አብነት ያስጀምሩት።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:13
msgid ""
"The plugin template is a "
"[cookiecutter](https://cookiecutter.readthedocs.io/en/stable/installation.html)"
" template that generates a plugin with the required structure and files. "
"This ensures that the plugin follows the expected structure and can be "
"easily installed into climweb."
msgstr ""
"የፕለጊን አብነት አስፈላጊው መዋቅር እና ፋይል ያለው ተሰኪ የሚያመነጭ አብነት "
"[cookiecutter](https://cookiecutter.readthedocs.io/en/stable/installation.html)"
" አብነት ነው። ይህ ፕለጊኑ የሚጠበቀውን መዋቅር መከተሉን እና በቀላሉ ወደ ክሊምዌብ መጫኑን ያረጋግጣል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:17
msgid ""
"To instantiate the template, execute the following commands from the "
"directory where you want to create the plugin:"
msgstr "አብነቱን ለማፍጠን፣ ተሰኪውን ለመፍጠር ከሚፈልጉት ማውጫ ውስጥ የሚከተሉትን ትዕዛዞችን ያስፈጽሙ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:24
msgid ""
"For more details on using the plugin boilerplate, you can follow the [step-"
"by-step guide](#plugin-boilerplate) on creating a plugin using the plugin "
"boilerplate."
msgstr ""
"ተሰኪውን ቦይለርፕሌት ስለመጠቀም ለበለጠ መረጃ፡ ተሰኪውን ቦይለርፕሌት በመጠቀም ፕለጊን ለመፍጠር [የደረጃ በደረጃ "
"መመሪያ](#plugin-boilerplate) መከተል ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:27
msgid "Plugin Installation API"
msgstr "Plugin Installation API"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:29
msgid ""
"A Climweb docker image contains the following bash scripts that are used to "
"install plugins. They can be used to install a plugin into an existing adl "
"container at runtime. `install_plugin.sh` can be used to install a plugin "
"from an url, a git repo or a local folder on the filesystem."
msgstr ""
"የ Climweb docker ምስል ተሰኪዎችን ለመጫን የሚያገለግሉ የሚከተሉትን ባሽ ስክሪፕቶች ይዟል። ፕለጊን ወደ ቀድሞ "
"አድል ኮንቴይነር በሂደት ጊዜ ለመጫን ሊያገለግሉ ይችላሉ። `install_plugin.sh` ፕለጊን ከዩአርኤል፣ git "
"repo ወይም ከአካባቢያዊ ማህደር በፋይል ስርዓቱ ላይ ለመጫን ጥቅም ላይ ሊውል ይችላል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:33
msgid ""
"You can find these scripts in the following locations in the built images:"
msgstr "በተገነቡት ምስሎች ውስጥ እነዚህን ስክሪፕቶች በሚከተሉት ቦታዎች ማግኘት ይችላሉ፡"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:35
msgid "`/deploy/plugins/install_plugin.sh`"
msgstr "`/deploy/plugins/install_plugin.sh`"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:37
msgid "On this repo, you can find the scripts in the `deploy/plugins` folder."
msgstr "በዚህ repo ላይ ስክሪፕቶቹን በ‹deploy/plugins› አቃፊ ውስጥ ማግኘት ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:39
msgid ""
"These scripts expect a ClimWeb plugin to follow the conventions described "
"below:"
msgstr "እነዚህ ስክሪፕቶች የClimWeb ተሰኪ ከዚህ በታች የተገለጹትን ስምምነቶች እንዲከተል ይጠብቃሉ፡"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:41
msgid "Plugin File Structure"
msgstr "ተሰኪ ፋይል መዋቅር"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:43
msgid ""
"The `install_plugin.sh` script expect your plugin to have a specific "
"structure as follows:"
msgstr "የ`install_plugin.sh` ስክሪፕት ተሰኪዎ በሚከተለው መልኩ የተወሰነ መዋቅር እንዲኖረው ይጠበቃል፡"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:55
msgid ""
"The folder contains three bash files which will be automatically called by "
"climweb's plugin scripts during installation and uninstallation of the "
"plugin. You can use these scripts to perform extra build steps, installation"
" of packages and other docker container build steps required by your plugin."
msgstr ""
"ማህደሩ ሶስት ባሽ ፋይሎችን ይይዛል እነዚህም ተሰኪውን በሚጫኑበት እና በሚራገፉበት ጊዜ በ climweb's plugin "
"ስክሪፕቶች የሚጠሩት። ተጨማሪ የግንባታ ደረጃዎችን፣ ፓኬጆችን መጫን እና ሌሎች በፕለጊንዎ የሚፈለጉትን የዶከር ኮንቴይነር"
" ግንባታ ደረጃዎችን ለማከናወን እነዚህን ስክሪፕቶች መጠቀም ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:59
msgid ""
"`build.sh`: Called on container startup if a runtime installation is "
"occurring."
msgstr "`build.sh`፡ የአሂድ ጊዜ መጫኛ እየተከሰተ ከሆነ በመያዣ ጅምር ላይ ይጠራል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:60
msgid ""
"`runtime_setup.sh`: Called the first time a container starts up after the "
"plugin has been installed, useful for running superuser commands on the "
"container."
msgstr ""
"`runtime_setup.sh`፡ ተሰኪው ከተጫነ በኋላ መያዣው ሲጀምር ለመጀመሪያ ጊዜ ይባላል፣ ይህም በመያዣው ላይ "
"የሱፐር ተጠቃሚ ትዕዛዞችን ለማስኬድ ይጠቅማል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:62
msgid ""
"`uninstall.sh`: Called on uninstall, the database will be available and so "
"any backwards migrations should be run here."
msgstr ""
"`uninstall.sh`፡ ማራገፍ ሲጠራ፡ ዳታቤዙ የሚገኝ ይሆናል እና ማንኛውም ወደ ኋላ የሚደረጉ ፍልሰቶች እዚህ መሮጥ "
"አለባቸው።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:65
msgid "The plugin info file"
msgstr "የተሰኪው መረጃ ፋይል"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:67
msgid ""
"The `climweb_plugin_info.json` file is a json file, in your root plugin "
"folder, containing metadata about your plugin. It should have the following "
"JSON structure:"
msgstr ""
"የ`climweb_plugin_info.json` ፋይል የ json ፋይል ነው፣ በእርስዎ root ፕለጊን አቃፊ ውስጥ፣ ስለ "
"ተሰኪዎ ሜታዳታ የያዘ። የሚከተለው የJSON መዋቅር ሊኖረው ይገባል፡"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:83
msgid "Expected plugin structure when installing from a git repository"
msgstr "የሚጠበቀው የተሰኪ መዋቅር ከ git ማከማቻ ሲጫኑ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:85
msgid ""
"When installing a plugin from git, the repo should contain a single plugins "
"folder, inside which there should a single plugin folder following the "
"structure above and has the same name as your plugin."
msgstr ""
"ከgit ላይ ፕለጊን ሲጭኑ፣ repo አንድ ነጠላ ፕለጊኖች ፎልደር መያዝ አለበት፣ በውስጡም ከላይ ያለውን መዋቅር "
"የሚከተል አንድ ፕለጊን ማህደር ያለበት እና እንደ ተሰኪዎ ተመሳሳይ ስም ያለው ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:88
msgid ""
"By default, the `plugin boilerplate` generates a repository with this "
"structure."
msgstr "በነባሪነት `plugin boilerplate` ከዚህ መዋቅር ጋር ማከማቻ ያመነጫል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:90
msgid "For example a conforming git repo should contain something like:"
msgstr "ለምሳሌ አንድ የሚስማማ git repo እንደዚህ ያለ ነገር መያዝ አለበት፡-"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:104
#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-boilerplate.md:1
msgid "Plugin Boilerplate"
msgstr "Plugin Boilerplate"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:106
msgid ""
"With the plugin boilerplate you can easily create a new plugin and setup a "
"docker development environment that installs adl as a dependency. This can "
"easily be installed via cookiecutter."
msgstr ""
"በተሰኪው ቦይለርፕሌት በቀላሉ አዲስ ፕለጊን መፍጠር እና አድልን እንደ ጥገኝነት የሚጭን የዶከር ልማት አካባቢን ማዋቀር "
"ይችላሉ። ይህ በቀላሉ በኩኪ መቁረጫ በኩል መጫን ይቻላል."

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:109
msgid "Creating a plugin"
msgstr "ተሰኪ መፍጠር"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:111
msgid ""
"To use the plugin boilerplate you must first install the "
"[Cookiecutter](https://cookiecutter.readthedocs.io/en/stable/installation.html)"
" tool (`pip install cookiecutter`)."
msgstr ""
"ተሰኪውን ቦይለር ለመጠቀም መጀመሪያ "
"[Cookiecutter](https://cookiecutter.readthedocs.io/en/stable/installation.html)"
" መሳሪያ (`pip install cookiecutter`) መጫን አለቦት።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:114
msgid ""
"Once you have installed Cookiecutter you can execute the following command "
"to create a new ADL plugin from our template. In this guide we will name our"
" plugin “My Climweb Plugin”, however you can choose your own plugin name "
"when prompted to by Cookiecutter."
msgstr ""
"አንዴ ኩኪኩተርን ከጫኑ በኋላ አዲስ የኤ ዲ ኤል ፕለጊን ከእኛ አብነት ለመፍጠር የሚከተለውን ትዕዛዝ ማከናወን ይችላሉ። "
"በዚህ መመሪያ ውስጥ የእኛን ፕለጊን \"የእኔ ክሊምዌብ ፕለጊን\" እንሰጣለን, ነገር ግን በኩኪ ቆጣቢ ሲጠየቁ የራስዎን "
"የተሰኪ ስም መምረጥ ይችላሉ."

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:119
msgid ""
"The python module depends on your chosen plugin name. If we for example go "
"with “My Climweb Plugin” the Django app  name should be my_climweb_plugin"
msgstr ""
"የ Python ሞጁል በመረጡት ተሰኪ ስም ይወሰናል። ለምሳሌ በ\"My Climweb Plugin\" ከሄድን የDjango "
"መተግበሪያ ስም my_climweb_plugin መሆን አለበት።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:130
msgid ""
"If you do not see any errors it means that your plugin has been created."
msgstr "ምንም ስህተቶች ካላዩ ይህ ማለት የእርስዎ ተሰኪ ተፈጥሯል ማለት ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:132
msgid "Writing a Plugin"
msgstr "ፕለጊን በመጻፍ ላይ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:134
msgid ""
"Now you have created a plugin, lets go into more detail of how to actually "
"extend and customize Climweb using your plugin."
msgstr ""
"አሁን ፕለጊን ፈጥረዋል፣ እንዴት በትክክል ፕለጊንዎን በመጠቀም Climwebን እንዴት ማራዘም እና ማበጀት እንደሚቻል "
"የበለጠ በዝርዝር እናስብ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:137
msgid "Storing State"
msgstr "ግዛትን ማከማቸት"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:139
msgid "If your plugin needs to store state, you should only ever do this in:"
msgstr "ፕለጊንዎ ሁኔታን ማከማቸት ካለበት፣ ይህንን በሚከተለው ውስጥ ብቻ ማድረግ አለብዎት፦"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:141
msgid "The database being used by Climweb"
msgstr "በ Climweb ጥቅም ላይ የዋለው የውሂብ ጎታ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:142
msgid "Using Django’s default storage mechanism"
msgstr "የጃንጎን ነባሪ የማከማቻ ዘዴ በመጠቀም"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:143
msgid ""
"The Redis being used by Climweb, but only for non-persistent state like a "
"cache that is fine to be destroyed at any moment."
msgstr ""
"Redis በ Climweb ጥቅም ላይ እየዋለ ነው፣ ነገር ግን በማንኛውም ጊዜ መጥፋት ጥሩ እንደሆነ መሸጎጫ ያለ ቀጣይነት"
" ላለው ሁኔታ ብቻ ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:147
msgid ""
"Never store any state in your plugin folder itself inside the container. "
"This folder is deleted and recreated as part of the plugin installation "
"process and any state you store inside it can be lost."
msgstr ""
"በእቃ መያዣው ውስጥ በራሱ ፕለጊን አቃፊ ውስጥ ማንኛውንም ሁኔታ በጭራሽ አታከማቹ። ይህ አቃፊ ተሰርዟል እና እንደ "
"ተሰኪው የመጫን ሂደት አካል ሆኖ እንደገና ተፈጥሯል እና በውስጡ ያከማቹት ማንኛውም ሁኔታ ሊጠፋ ይችላል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:151
msgid "Adding Python Requirements"
msgstr "የ Python መስፈርቶችን ማከል"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:153
msgid ""
"Your plugin is just a normal python module which will be installed into the "
"Climweb virtual environment using `pip` by `install_plugin.sh`. If using the"
" plugin boilerplate you can add any python requirements to the pip "
"requirements file found at `requirements/base.txt`."
msgstr ""
"የእርስዎ ፕለጊን በ`install_plugin.sh` በኩል `pip`ን በመጠቀም ወደ Climweb ምናባዊ አካባቢ የሚጫነው "
"የተለመደ የፓይቶን ሞጁል ነው። የፕለጊን ቦይለር ሰሌዳውን ከተጠቀሙ በ`requirements/base.txt` ላይ ባለው "
"የፒፕ መስፈርቶች ፋይል ላይ ማንኛውንም የpython መስፈርቶች ማከል ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:157
msgid "As a Django/Wagtail App"
msgstr "እንደ Django/Wagtail መተግበሪያ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:159
msgid ""
"When the Climweb Django service starts up it looks for any plugins in the "
"plugin directory. If it finds any it assumes the `src/plugin_name/` sub "
"folder contains a Django App and adds it to the`INSTALLED_APPS`. This means "
"that your plugin must be a Django/Wagtail app whose name exactly matches the"
" name of the plugin folder."
msgstr ""
"የ Climweb Django አገልግሎት ሲጀመር በፕለጊን ማውጫ ውስጥ ያሉ ማንኛውንም ተሰኪዎችን ይፈልጋል። ካገኘ "
"የ`src/plugin_name/` ንዑስ አቃፊ Django መተግበሪያ እንደያዘ እና ወደ INSTALLED_APPS' ያክላል "
"ብሎ ያስባል። ይህ ማለት የእርስዎ ፕለጊን ስሙ በትክክል ከተሰኪው አቃፊ ስም ጋር የሚዛመድ Django/Wagtail "
"መተግበሪያ መሆን አለበት።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:163
msgid ""
"In your plugin’s Django/Wagtail app you can do anything that you normally "
"can do with a Django/Wagtail app such as having migrations, using the "
"`ready()` method to do startup configuration etc."
msgstr ""
"በእርስዎ ፕለጊን Django/Wagtail መተግበሪያ ውስጥ እንደ ማይግሬሽን ያሉ በDjango/Wagtail መተግበሪያ "
"አማካኝነት ማድረግ የሚችሉትን ማንኛውንም ነገር ማድረግ ይችላሉ፣ የጅምር ውቅረትን ለመስራት የ`ዝግጁ()` ዘዴን "
"በመጠቀም።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:166
msgid "Publishing your Plugin"
msgstr "የእርስዎን ተሰኪ በማተም ላይ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/creating-a-plugin.md:168
msgid ""
"The easiest way to share you plugin with others is by making a `public` git "
"repository using GitHub,GitLab or some other git host. Once you have pushed "
"your plugin folder to the git repository then anyone can then install your "
"plugin following the steps in the Plugin Installation guide."
msgstr ""
"እርስዎን ፕለጊን ከሌሎች ጋር ለማጋራት ቀላሉ መንገድ GitHub፣GitLab ወይም አንዳንድ ሌላ git አስተናጋጅ "
"በመጠቀም `ይፋዊ` git ማከማቻ ማድረግ ነው። አንዴ የፕለጊን አቃፊዎን ወደ git ማከማቻው ከገፉ በኋላ ማንም ሰው "
"በፕለጊን መጫኛ መመሪያ ውስጥ ያሉትን ደረጃዎች በመከተል ፕለጊንዎን መጫን ይችላል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/index.md:1
#: ../../_docs/technical/index.md:28
msgid "Extending Climweb"
msgstr "Climwebን በማራዘም ላይ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/index.md:3
msgid ""
"At the base, Climweb provides a generic, well researched and tested content "
"structure that addresses most of the needs of the NMHSs, in providing a "
"functional and user-friendly website. This structure is designed to be "
"flexible and extensible, allowing for easy addition of services and products"
" provided by the NMHSs."
msgstr ""
"በመሠረቱ፣ ክሊምዌብ ተግባራዊ እና ለተጠቃሚ ምቹ የሆነ ድረ-ገጽ በማቅረብ አብዛኛዎቹን የኤንኤምኤችኤስ ፍላጎቶች የሚያሟላ"
" አጠቃላይ፣ በሚገባ የተጠና እና የተፈተነ የይዘት መዋቅር ያቀርባል። ይህ መዋቅር በኤንኤምኤችኤስ የሚሰጡ አገልግሎቶችን "
"እና ምርቶችን በቀላሉ ለመጨመር የሚያስችል ተለዋዋጭ እና ሊሰፋ የሚችል እንዲሆን ታስቦ የተዘጋጀ ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/index.md:7
msgid ""
"However, the needs of each NMHSs may vary, and some may require additional "
"features or customizations to meet their specific requirements. To address "
"this, ClimWeb can be extended by creating new modules, that we call "
"`Plugins`, which can then be integrated into the system."
msgstr ""
"ሆኖም፣ የእያንዳንዱ ኤንኤምኤችኤስ ፍላጎቶች ሊለያዩ ይችላሉ፣ እና አንዳንዶቹ ልዩ መስፈርቶቻቸውን ለማሟላት ተጨማሪ "
"ባህሪያትን ወይም ማበጀቶችን ሊፈልጉ ይችላሉ። ይህንን ለመቅረፍ ClimWeb አዳዲስ ሞጁሎችን በመፍጠር 'Plugins' "
"ብለን የምንጠራቸውን እና ከዚያም ወደ ስርዓቱ ሊጣመር ይችላል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/index.md:11
msgid ""
"These plugins can be used to add new features, modify existing "
"functionality, or integrate with external systems. These can be developed by"
" third-party developers, allowing for a wide range of customization options."
msgstr ""
"እነዚህ ተሰኪዎች አዲስ ባህሪያትን ለመጨመር፣ ያሉትን ተግባራት ለማሻሻል ወይም ከውጫዊ ስርዓቶች ጋር ለማዋሃድ ስራ ላይ "
"ሊውሉ ይችላሉ። እነዚህ በሶስተኛ ወገን ገንቢዎች ሊዳብሩ ይችላሉ, ይህም ሰፊ የማበጀት አማራጮችን ይፈቅዳል."

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-boilerplate.md:3
msgid ""
"With the plugin boilerplate you can easily create a new plugin and setup a "
"docker development environment that installs Climweb as a dependency. This "
"can easily be installed via cookiecutter."
msgstr ""
"በተሰኪው ቦይለርፕሌት በቀላሉ አዲስ ፕለጊን መፍጠር እና Climwebን እንደ ጥገኝነት የሚጭን የዶክተር ልማት አካባቢን "
"ማዋቀር ይችላሉ። ይህ በቀላሉ በኩኪ መቁረጫ በኩል መጫን ይቻላል."

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:1
msgid "Plugin Installation"
msgstr "ተሰኪ መጫን"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:3
msgid "There are a few ways to install a plugin:"
msgstr "ተሰኪን ለመጫን ጥቂት መንገዶች አሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:5
msgid "Using and environment variable"
msgstr "አጠቃቀም እና የአካባቢ ተለዋዋጭ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:7
msgid ""
"This method assumes you already have the Climweb docker compose services "
"running."
msgstr "ይህ ዘዴ ቀደም ሲል Climweb docker የሚሠራ አገልግሎት እንዳለህ ያስባል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:9
msgid ""
"You can use the `CLIMWEB_PLUGIN_GIT_REPOS` env variables when using the "
"Climweb docker images to install plugins on startup."
msgstr ""
"ጅምር ላይ ተሰኪዎችን ለመጫን የClimweb docker ምስሎችን ሲጠቀሙ የ`CLIMWEB_PLUGIN_GIT_REPOS` "
"env ተለዋዋጮችን መጠቀም ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:12
msgid ""
"The `CLIMWEB_PLUGIN_GIT_REPOS` should be a comma separated list of `https "
"git repo` urls which will be used to download and install plugins on "
"startup."
msgstr ""
"የ`CLIMWEB_PLUGIN_GIT_REPOS` በነጠላ ሰረዝ የተለየ የ`https git repo` ዩአርኤሎች ዝርዝር መሆን "
"አለበት ይህም በጅምር ላይ ተሰኪዎችን ለማውረድ እና ለመጫን ያገለግላል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:15
msgid ""
"After setting the environment variable, you can start the docker container "
"using the following command:"
msgstr "የአካባቢን ተለዋዋጭ ካቀናበሩ በኋላ, የሚከተለውን ትዕዛዝ በመጠቀም የዶከር መያዣውን መጀመር ይችላሉ."

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:21
msgid ""
"These variables will only trigger and installation when found on startup of "
"the container. To uninstall a plugin you must still manually follow the "
"instructions below."
msgstr ""
"እነዚህ ተለዋዋጮች የሚቀሰቅሱት እና የሚጫኑት መያዣው በሚነሳበት ጊዜ ብቻ ነው። ተሰኪን ለማራገፍ አሁንም ከታች ያሉትን "
"መመሪያዎች እራስዎ መከተል አለብዎት።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:24
msgid "Caveats when installing into an existing container"
msgstr "አሁን ባለው መያዣ ውስጥ ሲጫኑ ማስጠንቀቂያዎች"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:26
msgid ""
"If you ever delete the container you’ve installed plugins into at runtime "
"and re-create it, the new container is created from the base climweb docker "
"image which does not have any plugins installed."
msgstr ""
"ፕለጊን የጫኑበትን መያዣ በሂደት ላይ ከሰረዙት እና እንደገና ከፈጠሩት አዲሱ ኮንቴይነር ምንም አይነት ተሰኪዎች ከሌሉት "
"ከመሰረታዊ ክሊምዌብ ዶከር ምስል የተፈጠረ ነው።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:29
msgid ""
"However, when a plugin is installed at runtime or build time it is stored in"
" the `CLIMWEB_PLUGIN_DIR`which by default is `/climweb/plugins` container "
"folder which should be mounted inside a docker volume. On startup if a "
"plugin is found in this directory which has not yet been installed into the "
"current container it will be re-installed."
msgstr ""
"ነገር ግን፣ አንድ ፕለጊን በ runtime ወይም በግንባታ ጊዜ ሲጫን በ`CLIMWEB_PLUGIN_DIR` ውስጥ ይከማቻል፣"
" እሱም በነባሪነት `/climweb/plugins` መያዣ አቃፊ ሲሆን ይህም በዶክ የድምጽ መጠን ውስጥ ሊሰቀል ይገባል። "
"ሲጀመር በዚህ ማውጫ ውስጥ እስካሁን ባለው መያዣ ውስጥ ያልተጫነ ተሰኪ ከተገኘ እንደገና ይጫናል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:33
msgid ""
"As long as you re-use the same data volume, you should not lose any plugin "
"data even if you remove and re-create the containers. The only effect is on "
"initial container startup you might see the plugins re-installing themselves"
" if you re-created the container from scratch."
msgstr ""
"ተመሳሳዩን የውሂብ መጠን እንደገና እስከተጠቀምክ ድረስ፣ ኮንቴይነሮችን ብታስወግድ እና እንደገና ብትፈጥርም ምንም አይነት"
" ተሰኪ ውሂብ ማጣት የለብህም። ብቸኛው ተጽእኖ በመነሻ መያዣ ጅምር ላይ መያዣውን ከባዶ ከፈጠሩ ተሰኪዎቹ እራሳቸውን "
"እንደገና ሲጭኑ ማየት ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:37
msgid "Uninstalling a plugin installed using an environment variable"
msgstr "የአካባቢ ተለዋዋጭ በመጠቀም የተጫነ ፕለጊን ማራገፍ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:39
msgid ""
"It is highly recommended that you backup your data before uninstalling a "
"plugin."
msgstr "ተሰኪን ከማራገፍዎ በፊት የውሂብዎን ምትኬ እንዲያዘጋጁ በጣም ይመከራል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:41
msgid ""
"To uninstall a plugin you installed using one of `CLIMWEB_PLUGIN_GIT_REPOS`"
"  you need to make sure that you delete and recreate the container with the "
"plugin removed from the corresponding environment variable. If you fail to "
"do so and just uninstall-plugin using exec and restart, the plugin will be "
"re-installed after the restart as the environment variable will still "
"contain the old plugin"
msgstr ""
"ከ`CLIMWEB_PLUGIN_GIT_REPOS` አንዱን ተጠቅመህ የጫንከውን ፕለጊን ለማራገፍ ከተዛማጅ የአካባቢ ተለዋዋጭ "
"በተወገደ ፕለጊን መያዣውን መሰረዝ እና እንደገና መፈጠርህን ማረጋገጥ አለብህ። ይህን ማድረግ ካልቻሉ እና exec ን "
"በመጠቀም ፕለጊንን ብቻ ማራገፍ እና እንደገና ማስጀመር፣ የአካባቢ ተለዋዋጭ አሁንም የድሮውን ተሰኪ ስለሚይዝ ተሰኪው "
"እንደገና ከተጀመረ በኋላ ይጫናል።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:46
msgid "Checking which plugins are already installed"
msgstr "የትኛዎቹ ተሰኪዎች እንደተጫኑ በመፈተሽ ላይ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-installation.md:48
msgid ""
"Use the `list-plugins` command or built in /climweb/plugins/list_plugins.sh "
"script to check what plugins are currently installed."
msgstr ""
"በአሁኑ ጊዜ ምን ተሰኪዎች እንደተጫኑ ለማየት የ `list-plugins` ትዕዛዝን ወይም በ "
"/climweb/plugins/list_plugins.sh ስክሪፕት ውስጥ የተሰራውን ተጠቀም።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-overview.md:1
msgid "Plugin Overview"
msgstr "ተሰኪ አጠቃላይ እይታ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-overview.md:3
msgid ""
"ClimWeb Plugins are custom Wagtail apps that extend the functionality of "
"ClimWeb. They can be used to add new features, modify existing ones, or "
"integrate with external services."
msgstr ""
"ClimWeb Plugins የClimWebን ተግባር የሚያራዝሙ የWagtail መተግበሪያዎች ናቸው። አዲስ ባህሪያትን "
"ለመጨመር፣ ያሉትን ለማሻሻል ወይም ከውጭ አገልግሎቶች ጋር ለመዋሃድ ጥቅም ላይ ሊውሉ ይችላሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-overview.md:6
msgid "Some examples of what you can do with a Climweb plugin are:"
msgstr "በ Climweb ፕለጊን ምን ማድረግ እንደሚችሉ አንዳንድ ምሳሌዎች፡-"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-overview.md:8
msgid ""
"Add new country specific modules, for example for data processing, payments "
"integration etc."
msgstr "አዲስ አገር የተወሰኑ ሞጁሎችን ያክሉ፣ ለምሳሌ ለውሂብ ሂደት፣ የክፍያ ውህደት ወዘተ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-overview.md:9
msgid ""
"Add new page types that are not available in the core Climweb installation."
msgstr "በዋናው Climweb ጭነት ውስጥ የማይገኙ አዲስ የገጽ አይነቶችን ያክሉ።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-overview.md:10
msgid "Integrate with 3rd party APIs or software"
msgstr "ከ3ኛ ወገን ኤፒአይዎች ወይም ሶፍትዌሮች ጋር ያዋህዱ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-overview.md:11
msgid ""
"Install custom postgres extensions, system packages, python dependencies"
msgstr "ብጁ ፖስትግሬስ ቅጥያዎችን፣ የስርዓት ፓኬጆችን፣ የፓይቶን ጥገኞችን ይጫኑ"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-overview.md:12
msgid "And much more!"
msgstr "እና ብዙ ተጨማሪ!"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-overview.md:14
msgid "Important Notes on Plugins"
msgstr "በፕለጊኖች ላይ ጠቃሚ ማስታወሻዎች"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-overview.md:16
msgid ""
"You should always make backups of your Climweb data before installing and "
"using any plugin."
msgstr "ማንኛውንም ፕለጊን ከመጫንዎ እና ከመጠቀምዎ በፊት ሁል ጊዜ የ Climweb ውሂብዎን ምትኬ መስራት አለብዎት።"

#: ../../_docs/technical/extending-climweb/plugin-overview.md:17
msgid "You should only ever install plugins from a trusted source"
